	('Hard to use and skills can never be disable', 'xKiDzZ', 'iTunes', 1, 'This app is a complete disaster', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-10 05:04:19'),
	('tried around one hour and still get dead recursive call!!!', 'sssssstan', 'iTunes', 1, 'totally cannot login!!!', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-10 09:11:00'),
	('This app is very buggy!! I am so very tired of reading oops something went wrong...""', 'Sunshine09""', 'iTunes', 2, 'Not good', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-10 13:49:14');
