	(504, 'If it requires that I give it all the contacts in my phone then I don\'t want it. It should be that you add only the contacts you choose. Also not everyone wants the Alexa app. And if she\'s so smart then why do we have to memorize and tell her what skill she needs at that moment.', 'Zachary Bravo', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-23 00:00:00'),
	(505, 'The app won\'t let me complete setup. I get to that screen and it is blank. Nothing happens. What am I supposed to do? I\'ve uninstalled and reinstalled, same results...nothing.', 'Jodi Hawkins', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-23 00:00:00'),
