	(507, 'The recent update rendered the app unusable.  It\'s​ a shame. The device still works (in a now lesser capacity), as for the garage app itself.  One star.', 'J Free', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-23 00:00:00'),
