	(509, 'Probably the most sluggish and poorly developed app on my phone.  I can download, install, and open a list app from the play store before the Amazon Alexa shopping list loads.   Very disappointing from Amazon.', 'Jacob Bovatsek', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-24 00:00:00'),
