	(515, 'I love Alexa', 'Rhonda Tsesmelis', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-24 00:00:00'),
	(516, 'Changed from a 3 to 1 star. Now I\'m being forced to opt in to a call making feature. I just want to access my shopping list, the thing Alexa is useful for. I can no longer do that unless I want to be forced into another feature. Time to give Alexa the boot.  Previous and still accurate review: Way too slow. Also hate how every time I do anything I\'m supposed to tell Amazon if Alexa got it right. What should be plastered all over the home page. Disappointing...', 'Meghann Miller', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-24 00:00:00'),
	(517, 'My version has no help section,  but the website says it does. Alexa keeps telling me to go to help section.  Huh?', 'Matthew L', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-24 00:00:00'),
	(518, 'Didn\'t work!', 'Olivia Rausch', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-24 00:00:00'),
