	(521, 'Miserable app on my Samsung Galaxy S7 Edge.  The capabilities are pretty useful but on both my wife\'s phone and my phone it takes about a minutes to start and then is very sluggish in responding to scrolling and clicks.  Almost unusable.  We suffer through it weekly for our shopping list but once last year I tried opening it twice to get some responsiveness and discovered it had downloaded a gig of data.  Great idea and capability but miserable implementation in my limited experience.  Our Echo Dots, however, are pretty great and see daily use.', 'Ingenuity Research Corporation', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-24 00:00:00'),
	(522, 'This app was fine until the last update.  Now i don\'t know about some of the things other people have complained about in the updated app, but my main complaint is the list for shopping. It is messed up and it hides whatever is on the top of my list under the header.  Also it will no longer rotate when you turn your tablet or phone. Amazon needs to let anyone that wants to go back to the previous version until they get all the kinks out of this, go back.', 'Linda Moon', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-24 00:00:00'),
