	(540, 'This update is terrible!  Used to easily tell if what you said was correct.  Then could send feedback.  Searching for or browsing music was ok before... now just "thinks" or freezes.  Plays a random station. (Maybe because during think phase you accidentally touched one)  Want old one back and that was a 4/5.  This is TERRIBLE! 0/5.', 'J Lo', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-25 00:00:00'),
