	(563, 'I loved my Alexa - until it\'s update. It no longer connects to WiFi correctly no matter how times or methods you use to troubleshoot it. No WiFi means no Alexa... so my echo is just sitting obsolete pending developers fixes what wasn\'t broken in the 1st place to apparently roll out new add on\'s (i.e. call/ text feature) not too many are crazy about. The interface of the app and add-ons with the app seemed revamped & expanded but only got to browse around it less than a week before the Wi-Fi issue happened.', 'Jasmine Antuna', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-26 00:00:00'),
	(564, 'So far my echo is great!', 'Barbara Huggins', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-26 00:00:00'),
