	(566, 'Skills are lame, but it has promise', 'Carlos Baez', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-26 00:00:00'),
	(567, 'It has its quirks as in a certain game, Hangman, otherwise it\'s pretty good. I use it to access calendar, learning what each day is about  ("good morning, Alexa"); spelling, & alarms.  I still can\'t figure how to use the calling feature, I have the new Amazon Alexa but no where does it have to "link" people to the device, so how do I do this calling and messaging feature?  I just looked online what this "app" is supposed to look like, according to this website on Amazon Alexa; according to what is showing in the graphic pictures, I don\'t have any of that on my Samsung Galaxy phone.  All I can find on this app on my phone is the same selections as it was when I first downloaded it to my phone, nothing changed.  The App logo picture changed; that is all that has changed on my phone!  So, I CANNOT access that calling/messaging feature to connect my friends/family on Alexa to have Alexa call them!  Therefore I changed my rating of 4 star to a 3 star....I might even go to a 2 star if I can\'t do any of the updated features on my Samsung Galaxy phone!  Thanks alot!!!  You Amazon people didn\'t do me any good at all!!!', 'Carlene Carmen', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-26 00:00:00'),
	(568, 'Still can\'t get the alexa to alexa calling to work. Have called Amzon 2x and they can\'t figure out why either after several hours of phone tech service.', 'Carol', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-26 00:00:00'),
