	(578, 'I was loving my Echo Dot for music, podcasts, weather, random facts. But ever since this last update it\'s useless. Cant connect to WiFi and therefore doesn\'t work at all. I\'ve deleted the app and re-downloaded 5 times over the past couple weeks and it\'s still broken. Every time i try to connect my device to WiFi the app quits. I\'m super frustrated and just wish i hadn\'t allowed it to ever update bc then i could still be enjoying my background music and podcasts while cleaning the house =\\', 'Tess Taylor', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-26 00:00:00'),
