	(625, 'I mostly use this app to check song names, add new pandora playlists, or stop music when I\'m in another room. However, it\'s so painfully slow and the fact that I can\'t see what song is playing as soon as I start the app (like I used to be able to before the UI update) makes the whole process even slower and more frustrating :(', 'Jessica Weiller', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-27 00:00:00'),
