	(648, 'A serviceable but clunky app ruined. Opting out of conversations basically breaks the app. I DON\'T WANT TO GIVE YOU MY CONTACTS. So now I\'m sitting in a hotel unable to change the WiFi on my Tap because the app only does one thing: begs you to use the new messaging. Everything else INCLUDING the help menu option just spins forever.   This. App. Sucks.', 'Maggie McFee', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-05-28 00:00:00'),
