	(837, 'Good app, learning how to use. Once I learn each step, Alexa is very helpful. Especially for timers and reminders. Awesome for music. I\'m  sure as I learn each step she will become more and more helpful. Alexa and her app are awesome. Be patient, learn as you go!!!! You will like her I\'m sure.', 'Noreen Magana', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-05 00:00:00'),
	(838, 'The 2nd generation Echo Dot keeps disconnecting from the WiFi! Is it the place that it\'s sitting at? Or is it the Dot itself that can\'t hold the signal? This happens every morning that I come home, I have to put in setup mode.', 'BRAGGESTMOLD5 *', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-05 00:00:00'),
	(839, 'never opens. always force quit. i would give zero stars if i could. alexa sucks', 'Mark Sheppard', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-05 00:00:00'),
	(840, 'Love it', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-05 00:00:00'),
	(841, 'Won\'t let me go past the Setup stage, just has a blank screen. Please help!!', 'vince mnich', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-05 00:00:00'),
	(842, 'Alexa is good for quick, super easy info, but ohmygod is it awful for anything at all complicated. And having to shout over a song to tell the device to turn the music down has got to be one of the most frustrating first-world problems ever. Google manages to do it just fine, why can\'t the device figure out that someone shouting "ALEXA!" over the music is not part of the song?', 'David Soinski', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-05 00:00:00'),
	(843, 'Drains battery and performs very poorly - the lists are meant to work offline, but don\'t - what\'s the point of adding things to my shopping list if I can\'t access the bloody list at the supermarket!', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-05 00:00:00'),
	(844, 'epic asisstant ever', 'Oğuzhan Karkın', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-05 00:00:00'),
	(845, 'Love it!!!!', 'Tami Sandoval', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-05 00:00:00'),
	(846, 'My echo dot has disconnected from the internet and when I go to the setup page it just shows a white blank screen after I hit continue...😡', 'Elizabeth Heinze', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-05 00:00:00'),
	(847, 'OMG !!! IF I COULD GET THROUGH THE SETUP PART OF THIS I WOULD GIVE YOU A BETTER RATING. BUT THIS SUCKS. I REALLY THINKING OF RETURNING ALEXA AND BUYING GOOGLE HOME INSTEAD. THANKS AMAZON.', 'Alex Bernal', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-05 00:00:00'),
	(848, 'Won\'t work pn my Android phone', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-05 00:00:00'),
	(849, 'Idk I can\'t connect my thing', 'Verna Stonejackson', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-05 00:00:00'),
	(850, 'Takes to long to open', 'isaias Huacuz', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-05 00:00:00'),
	(851, 'The app just freezes since the latest updates. It\'s completely useless now.', 'Carrie Gunther', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-05 00:00:00'),
	(852, 'Gone from bad to worse. The Amazon echo dot disconnects from WiFi daily and since the update I can\'t even reconnect it because  I get to the language selection screen and there are no languages to select from so I can\'t proceed. I am quite close now to returning the device which is useless without working software to set it up!', 'Simon Dingley', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-05 00:00:00'),
	(853, 'Recent update broke much functionality, such as bluetooth sync.', 'Richard Charts', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-06 00:00:00'),
	(854, 'You guys updated the app but took out LANDSCAPE MODE? Not all of us use this app on a phone, we have tablets that we were using it with also in《landscape mode》just fine. Please put the real developers back on updates iinstead of handing it off to the interns like Google does on their updates. Thanks', 'Alan Michael', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-06 00:00:00'),
