	(864, 'Keeps losing WiFi and whenever I go into set up all over is a blank screen', 'Sean Walsh', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-07 00:00:00'),
	(865, 'Will not pair will any device for setup. If you can\'t set it up how are you supposed to use it? Please fix!', 'Lacey Roberts', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-07 00:00:00'),
	(866, 'I love the Alexa device And, if I was rating this app solely on its ability to visually show me what I ask Alexa, I would give a four star review. However, the problem is that whenever I try to actually utilize the app, it always lags. The lag is almost unbearable whenever I try to edit an alarm.', 'David Wohlgemuth', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-07 00:00:00'),
