	(871, 'I\'d love to give a detailed review but the app won\'t let me get far enough. It\'s just three lights, blinking at me endlessly. Tried reinstalling, clearing data and cache, even tried it on a different phone. Nothing. Nothing but three blinking lights. Forever.', 'Daniel Willett', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-07 00:00:00'),
