	(909, 'You guys are pathetic. You ruin a perfectly good thing only for your own personal game. I just bought my dot and it\'s useless without this app and now I can\'t do a single thing because it crashes on the setup. From what I\'ve read you guys ruined a perfectly good app and fixing this issue doesn\'t even look like a priority. I guess making money on something that can\'t be used without a crappy app is more important than actually providing a solution. You guys make me sick.', 'Manuel Vargas', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-09 00:00:00'),
