	(912, 'App won\'t work! Every since you did the app update and I had to re install app..it won\'t load ..just get the three dots moving like it\'s trying...yes I have uninstalled and re installed....cleared the cache ...not an idiot..it just doesn\'t work NOW', 'Kim Potts', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-09 00:00:00');
