	(960, 'It\'s hard to get it set up I get so far and I get stuck', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-12 00:00:00'),
	(961, 'Here are some helpful tips or troubleshooting that you can do if ever you are encountering some problems in your Echo devices:  *Connecting to your Wifi/Internet -make sure youre not connecting to a adhoc networks, and echo devices requires fast and stable connection so dont expect it to function properly if your connection isnt stable,  -Go to your alexa app&gt;menu (three horizontal lines at the upper left hand of the screen) &gt; settings&gt;choose your echo device&gt;update wifi and follow the steps in setting up your echo device -if you get an error message, make sure that you entered your wifi password correctly, restart your echo device, power cycle your router, reset if still not working or use a different device (even though some of your devices work properly with your wifi connection, the echo device is different, sometimes it depends on the compatibility of your router thats why you should check your ISP as well.)  *Echo device is not responding  -always check if the mic button on the echo device if it is RED because it means that its on MUTE and check on the alexa app if its offline or online.  -sometimes the echo device needs some refreshing, you can restart it by unplugging it from your power source and after full 20 seconds plug it back on again. -or you can move your device closer to your router -or you can power cycle your router -you can reset it as well but resetting the echo device is resetting everything and youre going to set it up again.    Learning is important and doing this basic troubleshootings can save time. Trust me this is based in experience and I know that this is frustrating and disappointing but still technology is not dormant so we should never stop learning as well. It may solve your issues and instead of calling support for this you can save your time :)   -Emblem.', 'Darlene Petilla', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-12 00:00:00'),
