	(1173, 'Does not work for my S7 Edge. App just freezes.', 'Melissa Malloy', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-23 00:00:00'),
	(1174, 'These features and I would\'ve given a 5 star. Being able to link my tunein account. The ability to remove favorited podcast/station in tunein, (You can add but not remove). Also the ability to use voice commands with tunein to play podcasts in chronological order from first episode to last. The use of voice commands to play certain episodes of podcasts. The ability to fast forward/rewind in epiodes of podcasts. Until these features are added there is no point to include tunein as an in app feature. It actually makes using the in app version very frustrating and as useful as any generic bluetooth speaker. Please and thank You.', 'Don Eldridge', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-23 00:00:00'),
	(1175, 'Update not workin, conversation icon not visible', 'Younqq Priince', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-23 00:00:00'),
	(1176, 'The app itself needs fine tuning. Pressing back doesnt take you back to your search page it takes you back to the home page. There could be a little description in each mini pic because selecting each one and then getting sent back to homepage when looking for a new skill gets old fast. The skills are mostly garbage too. Either not written well or really obscure things few people want/need. So far Alexas only useful if you already have a bunch of other things you pay monthly for and alexa binds them together. Not very interesting. Your phone already does that.', 'Michelle Richards', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-06-23 00:00:00'),
