	(1406, 'Drop In on Dots is 1 out of 5 stars. I\'ve got excellent bandwidth and an awesome wireless router. After getting the fancy email, I felt very excited about Drop In. Like when the update related for Zune revealing fancy new wireless functionality, it was like a bonus - remember?! Drop in however in my book, should never have been released in its current state. It\'s not solid, fades in and out, the volume is too low and uses the onboard speaker, breaking the bluetooth connection to that speaker, and is an embarrassment. I had someone excited to experience the new feature, but drop in was dropping out. I hope someone at amazon sees this post and explains why this was released when I\'d give it a 2 out of 10 for overall satisfaction. Disappointing.', 'Rick Castro', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-04 00:00:00'),
	(1407, 'I have to repeat myself a number of times before Echo Dot gets it right, plus the remote control unit does not work properly. Volume control is ok but microphone does not relay to the Dot , it cuts out before you finish what you are requesting.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-04 00:00:00'),
