	(1715, 'It would be a great app. If it didn\'t take me 1 whole minute to shut up the alarm using my phone. It\'s rediculous how much it lags. I press the alarm button and it lags about 10-15 seconds. Don\'t even think about pressing it again or you\'ll have 4 different alarms going off throughout the day while you aren\'t home. If you have dogs they will hate this feature.', 'Juan Zermeno', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-17 00:00:00'),
	(1716, 'Resource hog and it will not connect to Amazon music.   It used to just be very slow.  Now it won\'t connect at all.   I can still yell at my echo to play specific artists/albums; but browsing via the app does not work.   Funnily enough,  I can just use Firefox on my phone to visit the Amazon website, search music, and it will play on echo.   So... Why bother with the app at all?     I rated 2 stars only because I can use the app to pause Echo from anywhere.', 'Brian Watson', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-17 00:00:00'),
	(1717, 'Had Alexa and the original app working for several months. App updated and now won\'t run... Enter user name and password then get three dots and it sits there... No feedback, no error, no time out, just three dots animated left to right... Absolutely useless Amazon.... Running on HTC 10...tried deleting data, uninstall... worked fine previous to update!!! UPDATE July 2017 - APP STILL NOT WORKING, SORT THIS OUT AMAZON - USELESS', 'Stewart Rowbotham', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-17 00:00:00'),
