	(1722, 'This app is so slow and buggy. What prompted me to write the review was that there\'s no easy way to explore amazon music unlimited\'s options for artists. There are so many artists that a basic scroll  (which takes forever to load) makes it so hard to navigate. Additionally, the artists with "the" in the title are all listed under "the" alphabetically. There\'s no filtering in order to narrow it down to the artists you want. I think the purpose of this app is to help navigate all of the things Alexa can do for you, and it\'s so immensely frustrating. Work on this app, amazon!!', 'Rachel Wehr', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-18 00:00:00'),
