	(1813, 'Update: I\'m pretty sure that most of the recent one star reviews that say the recent updates made the app stop working are related to the latest Android system updates disabling the Android System WebView component and starting to use the Chrome browser for that function. So, Amazon, when are gonna fix this issue?', 'Russ Hampton', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-23 00:00:00'),
