	(1833, 'I love that there is an app that allows you to change settings and view what Alexa is playing at that moment.  However, the app is extremely slow. When I try to see what playlist she is playing or try to find a song or artist through the app, it just shows me three dots as if it were loading, but rarely brings it up and I just give up with frustration. I love my Alexa but the app could definitely use some improvements.', 'Jessica Gonzales', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-24 00:00:00'),
	(1834, 'So slow with everything. Stop trying to reinvent things with the music, just integrate the Amazon music app. I can\'t even browse or effectively use the music because it freezes trying to load the giant lists of songs or artists.', 'Travis Burton', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-24 00:00:00'),
	(1835, 'What a joke just got my echo today, thought I\'d set it up before I went to sleep 40 minutes later still sat waiting for the setup to launch. Will be putting it back in the box tomorrow and sending back.', 'BEN HOWE-HAYSOM', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-24 00:00:00'),
	(1836, 'Absolutely no way to search for artists or songs in Music Unlimited is RIDICULOUS. Add a search function!', 'Jeff Wassel', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-24 00:00:00'),
