	(1840, 'Cannot even setup my dot.  Worthless app.  Was finally able to do it on my fire.  Might end up returning the dot.', 'Laramie Mccue', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-24 00:00:00'),
	(1841, 'Amazon needs to do some serious upgrading on their app if they wish to even think about competing with Google. Forget the terrible AI that is Alexa (it makes Siri appear smart and that\'s a feat in itself), but just as an example: the app tried to synch my contact info. Ok fine, but I don\'t want all these people on Echo because well that\'s reserved for friends and family. But it won\'t let you delete them...ever. not manually, not automatically. After spending an hour with Amazon, their suggestion was to delete the contacts from my phone and let it resynch. Yes....delete scores of contacts because I don\'t want them on the cloud. I can\'t even make this up.', 'Bob Gohari', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-24 00:00:00'),
	(1842, 'I love it, especially for the music. Also like the list and for the reminder.', 'carolyn savoy', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-24 00:00:00'),
	(1843, 'Plugged in my Dot, it can\'t connect to the WiFi, and the Alexa app perpetually hangs just navigating to Settings.', 'Eric Bell', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-24 00:00:00'),
	(1844, 'Even Cortana is better than this', 'Mr Mike Provolone', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-24 00:00:00'),
	(1845, 'The app seems to think I\'m setting up the device every time I open it. I need to open it several times to get past this. It does not communicate with the other apps such as the to do list app which are needed to help it function. All in all a joke of an app. The actual echo device itself is hopeless as well as itjeeps cutting out and needs to be rebooted.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-25 00:00:00'),
