	(1853, 'Haven\'t received my Echo yet. Doesn\'t work at all with my Fire TV\'s. Apparently all it\'s good for is setting up the Echo, which doesn\'t look promising for the Echo\'s worth, and usefulness, why can\'t  you set it up by voice? At this point I honestly don\'t see why everybody is so crazy about this thing. Alexa on the Fire TV is not that useful. I think I  am wasting time and money, I have a suspicion that I should have gone another route at this point.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-25 00:00:00'),
