	(1856, 'This has gone on way to long, having to get rid of my echo because app DOES NOT WORK... It has been months since they updated the app and doesn\'t seem to be an end in sight. Please Amazon get on your dev team to fix this, too many people are having issues. At least give an option to go back to old version that worked.', 'Brandon Spurrier', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-25 00:00:00'),
	(1857, 'I wish the app would open to the home screen and not the conversations screen.', 'Jason Kosmiski', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-25 00:00:00'),
	(1858, 'Echo is a good device along with the two Dots I have but after doing the usual things like setting alarms and playing Amazon Music on them there is one big problem, they cannot play radio stations for more than 30 seconds. I ask Alexa to play BBC Radio 2 which starts up straight away, but about 30 seconds later, silence. If you ask Alexa to stop and then restart then the radio continues, so it has to be an Echo problem. I have ultrafast broadband and excellent wifi, so know that\'s not the problem.', 'John Bunyan', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-25 00:00:00'),
