	(1927, 'I LOVE THE AMAZON ALEXA APP AND ALL THAT YOUR NOW ABLE TO DO WITH IT. I WOULD HIGHLY RECOMMEND IT TO ANYONE ELSE WHO HAS AN ANDROID DEVICE, A CELLPHONE OR TABLET!!!!!!! I CAN HAVE IT READ AUDIBLE BOOKS TO ME, PLAY AMAZON UNLIMITED MUSIC FOR ME, ETC. ALL THROUGH THE ECHO DOT I BOUGHT FROM AMAZON. THE BEST INVESTMENT I COULD HAVE EVER MADE!!!!', 'William Reed', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-28 00:00:00'),
