	(1977, 'There are a couple of bugs in the system for this app. The app will not allow you to write a review and submit it nor can you set a defined search filter so you have to change it to user rating which because of the inability to write reviews, the apps have very little review about them. That\'s it, for now. As I find more bugs I will add them to this review.', 'Kenneth E. Koller', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-31 00:00:00'),
	(1978, 'App works great.  I use it with an Echo Tap.  It loads quickly on my old ass Galaxy S5 phone, and all of the features do what you\'d expect.  It\'s not meant to replace Google Assistant, but for controlling and using my Amazon devices, it\'s great.', 'A J', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-07-31 00:00:00'),
	(1979, 'The app keeps forcing you to the voice call setup menu even if you do not want the feature (no i will not sign up for it and then disable it later). Its reached the point where the app has become unusable because every time i want to alter a setting i am forced to go to the voice call setup menu and not allowed to exit it without shutting down the app. Utter garbage.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-08-01 00:00:00'),
	(1980, 'It would be really convenient to be able to stop alarms from the app when you\'re not in voice range.', 'Courtney Tompkins', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-08-01 00:00:00'),
