	(2007, 'I want to be able to scroll through songs. I want to be able to build playlists for songs in Amazon Music and podcasts in Tune In.   I want more podcasting capability. I want to be able to have a feed that I can manage with podcast search functions as well as paste functions for .rss feeds.   I want to be able to connect Echo Dot to Fire TV so I can trigger voice remote navigations and play functions for games and videos on Fire TV.', 'Lee S', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-08-03 00:00:00'),
