	(2062, 'Lacks useful search/filler for Alexa skills. Terrible UI,  e.g. grey on white  text. Only reason I keep it installed is the need to occasionally modify a setting that can\'t be done via the Alexa voice interface.', 'Paul Beltrani', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-08-06 00:00:00'),
