	(2102, 'Alexa is an absolute nightmare for AI and voice detection. Google Now is way more Superior when it comes to automation Alexa scenes bad at detecting things and I always have to repeat each command at least twice.', 'M B', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-08-10 00:00:00'),
