	(2106, 'The Alexa app is extremely clunky and slow. If the Echo loses its WiFi connection, you have to put it in setup mode, and wait, then the app tells you to connect manually by connecting to it directly, then you have to wait, then you get to select a WiFi connection, then you have to wait.....I think you get the drift. Thank God I bought the Echo at half price. I\'d really like to return it and get a Google Home.', 'Steve Evans', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-08-11 00:00:00'),
