	(2628, 'It\'s alright. Could do with a widget for my phone screen. Also Amazon music needs to be integrated better within the app. Still can\'t use the amazon music app to access playlist through Alexa.', 'Vikkie Everard', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-09-30 00:00:00'),
