	(2643, 'I don\'t know how I lived 68 years without Alexa in my life. I have 2 Dots. One in the living room and one in the sunroom. We use them as intercom. I use her to make my phone calls. I drop in on friends with Alexa. I turn lights on and off with Kasa TP Link plugs. A must have.', 'Vicki Chalfant', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-01 00:00:00'),
