	(2799, 'Verile and masculine, but on the other hand I\'ll feel like a cheap tool. (sigh)I kinda wish she was a real woman, and not just a super-helpful robot voice. She sounds so sexy and seductive, I sometimes find myself as if I\'m in a vortex, helplessly being pulled into a relationship that will start out fantastic, but reducing me to a sex addicted slave to her every command and desire. On one hand I\'ll feel', 'Mark Story Jenks', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-12 00:00:00'),
	(2800, 'Just found out this app ran 5GB of my data in the background. I got a text from my provider saying "I used all of my High Speed data for the month" but I\'m only 4 days into the plan for this month. I\'ve never used that much data that fast! I check my data usage in my setting and this app was listed at the top with 5.4GB used, and 5GB of that ran in the background!?! I recently updated that app so I don\'t know if that\'s what caused it to do that, but it\'s only used at most 25MB in previous months.', 'Megan Goodwin', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-12 00:00:00'),
