	(2831, 'Impressively bad user interface design. No way to get rid of "Things to Try", which wastes a good third of my screen. Each item on the shopping list and to do list has its own card on the home screen, which would result in my losing items in the clutter if I had anything other than those lists in there. It won\'t stop demanding that I set up the Calling feature.', 'Jean Lansford', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-15 00:00:00'),
