	(2838, 'Dear Amazon, I liked the app when it worked. Now it doesn\'t work. I don\'t like things that don\'t work especially if I\'ve paid for something that is supposed to work. The app now doesn\'t even show info when loaded despite being reinstalled several times it just shows the home button and the other button at the bottom of the screen, everything else is blank. Google are giving away a free Google home with the release of the pixel 2 at the end of the month. It would be a shame to lose customers because your app doesn\'t work...', 'Rob Williams', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-16 00:00:00'),
	(2839, 'Its getting better but some functions you read about take a longer time to reach the UK after the US version', 'Steve Harwood', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-16 00:00:00'),
