	(2843, 'It\'s awesome I change my alarm sound and it\'s tells me some quick tips I ask it good morning every day. It tells me a short quote and it gives me stuff to ask it.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-16 00:00:00'),
