	(2852, 'What had changed work the 17/10 update.? Still looking for voice recognition and routines. Amazon love to spam me about shopping with them but nothing on when these new services will be released. I could be another Google convert..', 'Peter Jones', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-17 00:00:00'),
