	(2854, 'If I go back when the app is trying to connect with my echo dot, it comes up with connection failed and I have to uninstall the app and start over from scratch. I\'ve had to do this multiple times.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-17 00:00:00'),
	(2855, 'Happy with it so far, but voice training, per se, is no longer available. Instead, it is said that \'the cloud\' learns from your previous utterances. Heuristic. Despite that, this wins hands down, since so much is available with it!', 'James Carlson', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-17 00:00:00'),
	(2856, 'i can\'t login!never!', '老非', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-17 00:00:00'),
	(2857, 'Works well  unless you\'re trying to link an account. Both any.do and TP Link kick you back to the app as soon as you sign in. Tried this now on two different Android devices and had the same experience. Works fine on the other major mobile platform though...', 'Paul Kerton', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-17 00:00:00'),
	(2858, '👍👍👍👍👍', 'Erick White', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-17 00:00:00'),
	(2859, 'Really like Alexa. I\'ve had no problems with it from activating lights and heating ,playing songs and asking about the weather.', 'alun talbot', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-17 00:00:00'),
	(2860, 'As others have stated, would like to see more app access', 'Michael McClary', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-17 00:00:00'),
