	(2862, 'The fact that I can\'t skip setting up the Messaging function is bull. Want to know how to get me to not use the app?? THIS is how!!', 'Kari Bluff', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-17 00:00:00'),
	(2863, 'Needs more information', 'Daniel Aguirre', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-17 00:00:00'),
	(2864, 'The new update makes the app unusable thanks to the calling feature it keeps telling me to set it up but I don\'t want to and i cant get out of it! Went from being a good app to and stupidly unusable app! So basicly I cant use the app or add skills at all. Devs need to sort this out now!', 'Joshua Hooton', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-17 00:00:00'),
	(2865, 'A solid companion app, Alexa holding its own in the current smart home device war with Google. Even pulling ahead.  I remain dismayed at the lack of parity when it comes to features outside of the UK. You will read about and possibly see features advertised in the UK that are only available in the US.', 'James Gorman', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-18 00:00:00'),
	(2866, 'Can\'t get past the screen wanting me to sign up for voice calls and messaging so Amazon can suck up all my contacts details without their knowledge or consent. This should be illegal, taking others people\'s details without their knowing. I am so angry with Amazon I\'m thinking of  cancelling my Prime membership and never buying from them again.', 'Colin Peck', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-18 00:00:00'),
	(2867, 'Don\'t listen to other reviews, the app works fine. People seriously don\'t have any idea how their technology works, its kind of sad. As for the calling feature, just add it, enjoy and STFU.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-18 00:00:00'),
