	(2906, 'Been trying to work out why my Note3 suddenly starting hanging and acting sluggish for first time in 4 years. Cleared memory, cleared caches including cache partition, loads of RAM and storage free, but still slow. Started deleting apps. No luck until I removed the Alexa app and hay presto phone has come back to life with no sudden hanging. Something in the latest Alex app update would appear to be killing my phone, not to sure what it\'s up to in the background, but it would appear to be doing something some even when it appears not to be running. Needless to say I\'ve left this app uninstalled.', 'Ade Green', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-22 00:00:00'),
