	(2914, 'Can\'t do a manual search for songs on this app. This is a basic thing that is needed as voice searcing often has to be too exact to find the right song and looking through a genre isn\'t a fast way to find a song. Also the the lag makes the app almost  useable.', 'Brian Anderson', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-23 00:00:00'),
	(2915, 'App was fine till they ruined it with the dumb mandatory set up of alexa to alexa voice chat. NO ONE CARES about this dumb feature...it\'s called a phone.', 'Juan hernandez', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-23 00:00:00'),
	(2916, 'Not sure , just got Alexa', 'Ramone Marquez', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-23 00:00:00'),
	(2917, 'App just shows a blank screen. Tried to reinstall but still no joy. Echo dot being returned to store tomorrow.', 'stuart walker', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-24 00:00:00'),
	(2918, 'Still holding off updating based on the consistently poor reviews. What is wrong with you Amazon, can\'t you just use some of that tax money you\'ve avoided paying and get this thing sorted or you\'ll have another Google convert. Previous review: Painfully slow to launch and needs to relaunch after a short time when not in use. Some buttons on the app do absolutely nothing, like/dislike music for example. Sluggish performance when moving between different sections. Not a well thought out interface for communication. I would instantly uninstall but you need this app for certain tasks.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-24 00:00:00'),
	(2919, 'Can\'t update location threw the app it just sets back to the original setup for it after about 5 seconds or after a house number and a beginning of the street it just automatically gose back to the default one even the zipcode cannot be typed in fast enough app is just ok.. Would be better if everything was easy to use and user freindly.', 'Matt Roop', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-24 00:00:00'),
	(2920, 'Stalls at phone list, does not work. May rethink use of Echo if no improvement.', 'Keith Mortimer', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-24 00:00:00'),
