	(2923, 'Make a phone with alexa, say "hang up", yell "hang up", scream "hang up", it don\'t hang up. I even tried saying the wake up word then "hang up" and it still don\'t hang up. Have to turn alexa off to hang up. Very annoying.', 'Edith Lowe', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-25 00:00:00'),
	(2924, 'The app keeps telling my android system needs to be updated, but my system is completely up to date. App won\'t open at all.', 'Jazz Loves Reborns', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-25 00:00:00'),
