	(2926, 'Very unreliable. It can\'t recognise the word \'kitchen, no matter what way I pronounce it. The app is dreadfully slow and can\'t find a single one if the dozen Sonos devices, even with Sonos skill installed. Poor show', 'Adam Hunniford', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-25 00:00:00'),
