	(2936, 'Disappointed! Amazon should be shamed. Such a wealthy company, not just in $$ but in technology, innovation and ability to hire the best in programmers yet the Alexa app sucks big time! The echo dot has incredible potential. I can tell by the responses I get when I ask certain questions. However, if it depends on the horrible app for its skills as an AI, it\'s getting no where slowly with each update. I really want to like the Echo and I\'m hanging on Alexa but... I may have to find another girl. Come on Amazon, you can do better!', 'Ibis S', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-25 00:00:00'),
	(2937, 'It does not even recognize the country I live in. It\'s simply not available in the options. Still way to go.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-25 00:00:00'),
