	(2942, 'Slow, buggy and inconvenient to use. There is still a lot of work to with this app. Edit 07/03/2017: the app is a lot more stable now. But basic features like search option within music unlimited section are still missing.', 'Henry Rollin', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-26 00:00:00'),
	(2943, 'This worked great until a few days ago. Now it will not load properly. It will not let me select anything to use. For example, I could choose any song/album to play. Now it will not load the section. I could also change the alarm, now that section will not load. Hopefully this is fixed soon.', 'Heather Horn', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-26 00:00:00'),
	(2944, 'Most things are good, but it needs a way to manually add contacts that don\'t automatically show up.', 'Glenn Iverson', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-26 00:00:00'),
