	(3016, 'Amazon, why have you outsourced your app to a third rate developer , an app that crashes, is clueless & is buggy to the core .Nothing is working, it\'s as if it was hurriedly launched in India without any checks & tests . Worthless !', 'George Rebeiro', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-30 00:00:00'),
	(3017, 'Good app', 'Lane Watts', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-30 00:00:00'),
	(3018, 'I just would like to play music I like every day from a certain time. First there is no such routine setup option in this app. Second the music selection on Unlimited Prime is actually very limited. No way to customize the list. No search. Just a preconfigured set like fast-food. If Amazon is truly the most user aware company on the earth, do right now to shift all the development resources to get it to the state what it should be. Otherwise it will be paid back in an undesirable manner.', 'Ichiro Ishiguro', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-30 00:00:00'),
