	(3020, 'Doesn\'t even do that it does in the commercials. False advertising.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-30 00:00:00'),
	(3021, 'Until the most recent update this app worked perfectly for controlling my lights along with my Amazon Echos. Since the update, the echo keeps reporting that it was unable to make the lighting adjustments I requested successfully and yet it actually does make the adjustment. Similarly, where as the lights used to fade out when I made the request via the Echo they now abruptly turn off. This is all since the most recent update. Please investigate, I use this daily and I\'d like the functionality to be back the way it was.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-10-30 00:00:00'),
