	(3037, 'This NEEDS to be able to connect to 802.1x networks! I have many friends in university that were really interested in buying one but can\'t because it wouldn\'t connect to the network. I also brought mine from home and was deeply disappointed finding out that I can no longer use mine at all because it can\'t connect to the network.', 'Daniel Reynolds', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-01 00:00:00'),
