	(3074, 'It works okay, but there\'s a major issue with a cookie bug.  If you\'re logged in to Amazon in another Amazon app (Amazon Shopping, etc) most of the time the Amazon Alexa app will not open. Instead, it just sits there with the loading icon spinning.  The fix (until the programmers eliminate the bug), which took me forever to find online, is to open other Amazon apps, logout of Amazon, then open Alexa.', 'Steve - W.O.W.', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-02 00:00:00'),
	(3075, 'Good one, but needs to improve a lot, hope Amazon will live up to it\'s standard.', 'Chandra Shekar', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-02 00:00:00'),
	(3076, 'I can\'t connect fire TV with echo using this app as there no options in the app, while the Amazon site says there should be.. seems like they have not rolled out this feature worldwide but only to a small controlled audience', 'Vivek Mehra', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-03 00:00:00'),
	(3077, 'Not working with My Echo first gen!! Skills for India are inaccessible!!', 'Ashootosh Bhardwaj', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-03 00:00:00'),
	(3078, 'No option for local Adress in India for my echo dot. My location shows in Seattle and weather of Seattle. And in music there is no option like savan etc which was promised before shipping by Amazon and no Amazon prime music app in play store. Overall very disappointed.Hope India specific update come soon and prime music also on Indian play store.', 'himanshu pathak', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-03 00:00:00'),
