	(3084, 'Just keeps getting better, amazon keep finding new and innovative ways to make their echo family smarter. I though I\'d commend them now before Google throw another toy out if the pram and remove the app from the play store like he big baby\'s did by removing YouTube from the echo show. The only thing Google did there for me was cement that I never want to own one of their home devices now!', 'Steven Watson', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-03 00:00:00'),
