	(3086, 'Echo device is quite responsive. However, the app isn\'t. It takes a lot of time to load the content. Amazon you have wonderful cloud computing. Wondering why this app is so so sluggish in India. The features in app look basic or incomplete. Please curate the skills, loads of useless skills.', 'Naveen Kulkarni', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-03 00:00:00'),
