	(3096, 'I bought an echo dot, downloaded the app but  Am very disappointed  with the app. So many things don\'t work and many functions missing, like I cannot connect to my fire t.v stick, no option to make calls and messages , kindle dosent work and many more. All these work fine in other countries so why not in india. Am sure an update will change things. So waiting eagerly for an update.', 'priyesh khara', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-03 00:00:00');
