	(3117, 'There cannot be any background noise or else I literally have to yell before retaining any confirmation for my request and what I\'m told from "Alexa" normally doesn\'t comply with my command or is completely misunderstood for a ridiculous question that no one would ever ask.     Occurs when the tv is at a minimal volume or any one else is talking plus I cannot ask important things like what the gas prices are. Maybe the Google Home will, I\'ll be sure to update once I test it out & if that works better I will be sure to deactivate my Echo then reduce my 3* rating to 1*.', 'Austin Russell', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-04 00:00:00'),
