	(3125, 'Ironic: I need to Google how to fix this damn thing!  It works as long as you don\'t want to make changes after initial setup. Changing/resetting devices is a HUGE P.I.T.A. Even with a "factory reset" Love Amazon for shopping, but their devices need cleaning up. I think they overreached here.', 'Christy Kniseley', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-05 00:00:00'),
