	(3166, 'The latest update is almost there, we just need to be able to specify when something is a light so telling Alexa to turn on the lights will work fully. Currently, if the device isn\'t classified as a light, it won\'t turn on when  telling alexa to turn on the lights, even if light or lamp is in the name.', 'William Steele', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-07 00:00:00'),
	(3167, 'Was a great App until the last "upgrade", now it just drains my battery.  Update.. so disapointed that I really am selling my echo.  Amzn screwd up. Makes me sad. I do not recommend the Echo anymore.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-07 00:00:00'),
