	(3300, 'UPDATE: 15.11.17 The App is getting worse. Very very slow......and now I\'ve got no skills or music....I spend nore time speaking to  Amazon than i do the wife.....I\'m getting fed up of talking to Amazon....way too big to be excellent....   ORIGINAL: This reviewew is Only on the Echo.....not the "echo dots as they are VERY POOR"...the Echo is Better than when it started. It really needs phone linking. To rival Google.....good sound. Great at understanding. I\'ve had the echo since it was pre order.  So good I ordered 2 dots they have never got better at anything....what a waste of money. I\'ve just pre orderd a new echo. Second gen.....UPDATE it got delivered to someone else, no delivery card....what a going on...they had to send another, one. Its here, it\'s as good as the Original although it\'s not working at the moment. None of the skills or music. On the whole house and we have 4 in total..... You need a voice like Pavarotti to get the dots to work  I think the dots would work well in space....just floating.........heading towards the sun. Be way more entertaining!! If they were captured by the Borg, they wouldn\'t be able to do anything with them....', 'Jason Stockhill', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-14 00:00:00'),
	(3301, 'Started out great...   Is nothing but trouble now.  Alexa no longer can control any of the smart plugs I have... (15 of \'em)  ...was working wonderfully for weeks...  But last week all the smartplugs became "unresponsive" (according to Alexa), disabling and re-enabling the skill has fixed this issue in the past, but no longer... Alexa can find them, but not control them... So now I have to reach down to where these lights are plugged in to turn them off and on now... (Or, find the phone, load the app for the smartplugs, and turn them on/off from there)   ... The -Alexa- app still says they are "unresponsive"....  Investing in Alexa was a mistake.  A very expensive one.  Lesson learned.', 'Todd Kennelly', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-15 00:00:00'),
