	(3369, 'We\'re still far away from mastering this future tech. It works some times and even less with other "alexa enabled" devices. I had to buy a range extender just to use it in my bedroom, still debating if it was worth it. My latest issue is I cannot write a review for Alexa skills without it being blocked by my keyboard, and it always refreshes whenever I leave the app. I\'m also having an issue with duplicate smarthome devices appearing and changing the names doesn\'t work at all. This thing is useless.', 'Stephen Govea', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-18 00:00:00'),
