	(3374, 'Incredibly slow, I assume it goes back to Amazon\'s servers for EVERY little thing.  This app really hurts my perception of my Echo and Tap which are likewise really slow for what I assume is the same reason.  Why on earth can\'t the app talk directly to the device sitting 3 feet away on the same WiFi & Bluetooth networks? Also, NO, I\'m not giving it access to my contacts, no matter how much it nags me.  Wish I didn\'t have the app, the Echo, or the Tap.', 'Michael Galassi', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-18 00:00:00'),
