	(3411, 'Needs improvements', 'Arin H.', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-21 00:00:00'),
	(3412, 'The Alexa does nothing that was advertised when I bought it. It can, if you buy various descriptions, but that was not shown in the ads, and should have been included in the purchase price, as implied by Alexa\'s advertising. For the exorbitant overpriced purchase I made, I basically have an ugly paperweight that tells me the weather. Alexa does not play music for me, not even my YouTube playlist, does not turn on and off my lights, or do any of the features shown in its television marketing. I feel like I have suffered the biggest scam of the century. Horrible, horrible product!', 'Michael Lauinger', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-21 00:00:00'),
	(3413, 'Before the update this was intuitive and easy to navigate, a real joy to use.   After the update it\'s a pain to work with and so sloooow to start up and to top it off some of the skills don\'t work anymore.  The Smart home shows devices multiple times, disabling the skills for the bridges does nothing to remove them. Even uninstalled and reinstalled the app does nothing to remove them. Some groups do not work no matter if you include the duplicate devices.   I dread going into the app now well done Amazon NOT!', 'Mark Robbins', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-21 00:00:00');
