	(3422, 'Alexa will be better when all the skills are auto enabled. Each skill should have a casual wake up sentence. For example, if I want Alexa to search a recipe, she cannot do! I should tell the skill\'s name and exact command of the skill to perform the required action. As an average human, I cannot remember more that 10 specific messages of the skills!', 'Imran Kumbhojkar', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-11-22 00:00:00'),
