	(3612, 'only useful for keeping a shopping list. unless you have mostly quiet household, not with little kids, ha! cause alexa misunderstands much more often then not with the slightest noise in the background.  in the shipping list part of this app, used to be able to listen to what was originally said, but that feature got taken out.  why? now, without knowing what I originally did say, I can\'t use this for any practical purpose whatsoever.  what a waste', 'Katya Dennis', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-03 00:00:00'),
