	(3619, 'Needs to go a long way to better its services. As against claims of high Sensitive mic, in noisy background, it doesnot listen. we have to shout. Getting done what we want is very Cumbersome. Switching between wifi is long process. Easy switching should be there. Dot needs a cheaper power base. The power base available now are costlier than Dot', 'Venkatesan G.V.', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-03 00:00:00'),
	(3620, 'This update won\'t work. It keeps telling me to update the Android System Web View, but this is already updated. Tried uninstalling both, and reinstalling, but no avail. So in effect, I now have numerous Alexa devices that I cannot manage. Badly disappointed.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-03 00:00:00'),
	(3621, 'Works well. Not problems so far', 'Alan Mainwaring', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-04 00:00:00'),
