	(3623, 'Fantastic, love it', 'lee simms', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-04 00:00:00'),
	(3624, 'Does exactly what it says on the tin! Having Alexa say goodnight is a very pleasant thing indeed!! I can\'t get the image of her in a room on her own talking to everyone (a la Big Bang Theory), soooo sad!', 'Jo Llewelyn-Brinsley', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-04 00:00:00'),
	(3625, 'I loved this app.. I could call my son whilst I\'ve been working away.  Since the update, I can no longer connect to the servers so can no longer use the two echo devices I bought for the purpose I bought them for!  Fix it please and I\'ll gladly give you a 5* rating', 'jon gisicki', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-04 00:00:00');
