	(3633, 'The alexa app its self is trash. The font is too small. The text fields don\'t work, and if they\'re at the bottom of the screen they get blocked from view by the keyboard.  It won\'t support multiple amounts on one household.  The integration to sonos feels half-assed. It doesn\'t seem to support our first generation sonos.  It doesn\'t do volume control very well.   The voice recognition vocabulary is incredibly whitewashed.  "Play Phife Dawg Radio" "Sorry I could not find five dogs radio on Pandora "', 'bryant ho', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-04 00:00:00'),
	(3634, 'Horrible 505 error, dont have this problem w other apps.  Echo dot wont work without it', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-04 00:00:00'),
	(3635, 'Can\'t see any skill to control my fire tv. C\'mon amazon, if you can do that in US, u can do the same in India as well.', 'Deepak Rajput', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-04 00:00:00'),
	(3636, 'Its ok...', 'Hank smith', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-04 00:00:00'),
	(3637, 'It was a great app. In the Music, Book and Video drop down I was able to select all genres of music and artists but now I\'m unable to find any of it. The app freezes a lot.', 'Mark Webb', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-04 00:00:00'),
	(3638, 'The best', 'Fred Ang', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-04 00:00:00'),
	(3639, 'Why only allow 2 household users!? We have more than 2 people in the house that want to use the app to add their own shopping lists etc. It makes it literally pointless for anyone else to install the app.    Also it should recognise different voices instead of having to switch profile, stupid.   Stupid as hell. Learn a thing or two from Google, they don\'t restrict you like this.  Oh and the app is too slow to navigate.', 'Tom Cooper', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-05 00:00:00'),
	(3640, 'Alexa is great.', 'adriano raffaele', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-05 00:00:00'),
	(3641, 'I am not able to link my Fire TV Stick & Echo. Also performance of the app is poor.', 'Vijo Varghese', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-05 00:00:00'),
	(3642, 'Need to be optimised for Indian users. I try to listen to music on my echo dot, but prime music doesn\'t have much Hindi, Telugu, Tamil music collection.  Should expand the music Indian music library in prime music. I couldn\'t add address of an location in Hyderabad. So lot of features like traffic, weather updates are not available to me. It\'s been just a day of usage. I will update review with shortcomings in future as I use.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-05 00:00:00'),
