	(3654, 'Not able to setup on Android.  I m using gen1 echo with Android Oreo device. I tried it to setup on my phone but it didn\'t work. I tried all options like turning off smart Wi-Fi connection, resetting Echo device But no luck. I think gen1 echo no longer works. Wasted my money on this $100 paper weight..', 'Pranav Buradkar', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-05 00:00:00'),
