	(3690, 'Amazon refuses to let uses remove items from a list stating security reasons, yet anyone can add to a list.   This is b.s..  also they took away the ability to remove items from your smart home and replaced it with a disable option.  Stop taking away things we need and refusing to provide is with the options we want.  We purchased the product,  not your high and mighty opinion.  You have turned a useful smart home interface into a garbage collecting bin which you will probably use to try to shovel more you wanted items down our throats. Knock this off or I\'ll be switching over to Google home.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-07 00:00:00'),
