	(3910, 'So sad, the more popular this has become the worse the functionality of it-  more software problems.... and slow to fix.  Example: Looping streaming music from Amazon. Wondering if their IT infrastructure is overwhelmed or poor code, etc. Not worth paying for unlimited family music with lack of a fix.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-18 00:00:00'),
