	(3921, 'It can tell you the time yay everything else "not supported in your country" or "not supported on this device" it\'s not supported on even Amazon devices it\'s stupid. Stick to google, siri, Bixby or cortana because Alexa is like talking to a stubborn mental patient with severe learning difficulties.', 'Chris Hesketh', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-18 00:00:00'),
