	(4035, 'I love my Alexa devices 4 dots; 2 shows & 2 fire tv sticks.  The app is excellent.  I have routines set. Groups set. And multi room music.  I would like to set up more than one multi room music group (eg. Downstairs vs upstairs vs everywhere). The only real issue I have at the moment is using as an intercom (drop in). The only names it recognizes are those in my contacts but the devices themselves our not contacts and Alexa dies not recognize them by "device name". Frustrating as I love this feature.  I can drop in using the app without issue. It\'s just from device to device that has issues. If this is fixed I would give it a 5 stars. Keep up the great work Amazon.', 'Crystal Ketwaroo', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-22 00:00:00'),
