	(4041, 'Great app', 'Michael Jary', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-23 00:00:00'),
	(4042, 'After last update alexa wont control sonos or heating, thanks. All devices still showing up but reports nothing in that room to control heat or play music. Why is this app so slow. Why no full integration with sonos like when you pair with bluetooth speaker so all audio is directed to the sonos speaker and not the echo, this may be also a sonos issue. It would be better if the integration was full as you would get with the new sonos speaker. Come on amazon move this app on, ive a echo plus and hub functions are very basic need to be able to trigger music play back on devices in routines for a start.', 'Rich Hyde', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-23 00:00:00'),
	(4043, 'I have Samsung\'s new flagship phablet and your app doesn\'t work with it so it\'s total garbage. The part that doesn\'t work is the calling feature that\'s the entire reason why I have a phablet. You need to consult the higher-ups and figure out why you don\'t allow calling on phablets. It\'s a gross oversight.', 'Jayadev Bhakta', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-23 00:00:00'),
