	(4335, 'The app is great and works perfectly. I use it with my new echo dot. I love how alexa can tell me stories, play games, and play my music.  I just wish alexa could remove items from my lists. I don\'t want to have to take out my phone every time I complete a task. Other than that, this app is 5 stars.', 'Eve Loehrer', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-27 00:00:00'),
