	(4349, 'Won\'t install, like most other Amazon apps.', 'Chad Swift', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-27 00:00:00'),
	(4350, 'Wow .horrible isn\'t the word android and alexa are not compatible.  App is a joke can\'t log in even with multiple successful password resets.really thinking of sending it back.its so  underwhelming. though i would be a smart ass showing off to the family in Christmas day instead I\'ve just sat for hours trying to get it to work.its the worst interface on an app ever.please Amazon bin it or totally reinvent it.', 'Andy Offless', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-27 00:00:00'),
	(4351, 'Works perfectly for me! Got my first dot and used this app as a 100% alexia newby novice, it done everything perfectly. Easily connected light bulbs, plug sockets, speakers and the voice remote first time with no problems, all as it was meant to with the instructions.  5* on all fronts! Absolutely lovin my smart home! Highly recommended!', 'Flick Zverko', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-27 00:00:00'),
	(4352, 'Love Alexa', 'Bryan Mead', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-27 00:00:00'),
	(4353, 'I think this app supports an incredible device, but they sure could use some help with app. It is clunky looking, but I suppose Amazon is more about things that work than looking perfect.', 'Jordan Harmon', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-27 00:00:00'),
