	(4357, 'The echo dot is great but this app is a prime example of bad design, maybe Amazon should develop regular android and fire versions separately.', 'Abhineet Dubey', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-27 00:00:00'),
