	(4359, 'App is totally useless...i am very very tech savvy..app refuses to work with my phone or pc...can not even connect to WiFi at all. Sad because the echo was a gift and will need to be returned..just happy I didn\'t go and purchase the echo plus like I planned on. Could only imagine the nightmare that would be to set up. Back to the store with this paperweight!!', 'B. Cot', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-27 00:00:00'),
	(4360, 'App features are horrible. Will not connect.', 'MrClutchclutch', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-27 00:00:00'),
