	(4362, 'I thought from this app\'s title and description that I install Alexa. Wrong, it is just companion app for echo devices', 'Ciprian Stanescu', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4363, 'Does this app support Alexa show device control ? it\'s showing offline even tho it\'s physicaly connected to the net ? ....From my research this has been an issue for a long time with most devices? Could we have a update or an fix please ? Cheers Stu', 'Stuart Nickels', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4364, 'Excellent companion app for Echo devices.', 'Hillol Debnath', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4365, 'I love it 🐩🐩🐩🐩', 'ms. Jae Salas', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4366, 'Good app overall but needs further refining. Echo devices cannot be used in more than one multiroom groups. The lists are not particularly user friendly. Take as an example that you cannot edit an existing line. You have to delete the whole text and rewrite it.', 'Nick B', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4367, 'The app is fine.  The lack of instructions on how to do anything is frustrating.  You have to keep downloading extra apps to make things work with the echo.', 'Clos Graddfa', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4368, 'I can barely scroll through the Amazon Music selection, as it\'s too laggy (this is on my Note 8), unoptimized, and lacks a search feature for some reason. The rest of the app is not much better. With the amount of resources Amazon is putting into their Echo department, their app integration of the otherwise solid product that is the Echo leaves a lot to be desired. You have to link the app up with your Echo so it\'s not like you have a choice anyway. I usually only use my Echo for Bluetooth and alarms so thank goodness I rarely have to use the Alexa app.', 'Miles Braxton', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4369, 'Pure junk, doesn\'t work at all.', 'Andrew Swain', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4370, 'Just saying discovery failed when trying to connect to hue bulbs', 'Antony dyson', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4371, 'It works again!', 'Matthew Borchers', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4372, 'This app is missing more commands. Good start to AI', 'Ernest Lawson', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
