	(4376, 'Cannot get it set up on my Android phone.  It keeps telling me to "turn off auto network switch" which cannot be located on my Samsung 5. HELP!!!', 'John Hastings Sr', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00');
INSERT INTO `rating` (`id`, `review`, `author`, `review_source`, `rating`, `title`, `product_name`, `reviewed_date`) VALUES
	(4377, 'It\'s was way to slow to load.real slow', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4378, 'I love Alexa, so helpful. But, the app completely  broken my phone. I can record anything without it sounding high pitched, any videos or music I try to watch do the same thing. I actually liked the app, so disappointed it turned out to be a waste of space and time.', 'Crystal Ruby', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4379, 'Alexa is amazing', 'Georgia Topham', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4380, 'This typical Amazon deployment, tripping over themselves to force something out too early, falling on their sword and then playing catchup to do damage control. They dont seem to do much of anything roght thst doesn\'t alienate 1/2 their customer base. It\'s not working on Samsung Note 3. It should have NEVER been released in this condition. Please fix it yourself and stop using your users to debug and troubleshoot it for you, or at least list it properly as Beta or Early Release and not subject us to this aggravation without prior warning?! M-kay? No way this passed Beta release. If it did, the entire team is lying and should be fired. What a joke! Does it work for anyone?', 'Paul Lewis', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4381, 'Smart technology is absolutely addictive, but Alexa has a few issues.  Overall, however, I love my Echoes, and I\'m hoping Amazon will keep improving the software.  The issues:  Commands that work right one day don\'t work the next.  This is  especially true of commands she sends to my harmony hub, but is true for simple things like "play x song" as well.  There are also some limitations I\'d like to see addressed.  I\'d like her yo work with Netflix on the firestick and I\'d like to be able to use the multiroom feature with Audible.', 'Michelle Lock', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4382, 'I do not have a video music and books section at all.', 'Harneet Gawera', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4383, 'Stupid', 'still PanDaZ', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4384, 'Unable to find many local skills in the Alexa App. Where are all local news channel, Ola, Zomato. No search results found at all.', 'Swanand Panchi', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4385, 'I just started using this app with my dot and so far I\'m effing thrilled. ☺', 'S Johnston', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4386, 'Unable to install on my Note 5.', 'Sandra Waller', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4387, 'I DON\'T WANT TO DO MESSAGING. This may be a great option if you live alone, but I have 6 people in my household, and I DO NOT want to set up messaging. I can\'t run the app any more. I do not want Alexa to get to know me better - I want to add a new skill. Please fix this.', 'Paul Barnes', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4388, 'Ability to play an album or a song of my choice using music service as an action in the routine section of the application would certainly help.', 'Divya Prakash', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4389, 'Just takes a little bit of time to set up but once you get everything setup it works well', 'Ray R', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4390, 'This app does not give me the option too add another account. agrrr', 'Mark Fensom', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4391, 'Amazing best ever', 'Stephora', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4392, 'Fun app, although there are it\'s downsides.', 'Jaedon B.', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4393, 'It will not let me connect to the Amazon internet portion of the setup. My Wi-Fi has excellent connection. I don\'t k ow what the hell to do.', 'Andrew Kohl', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00');
INSERT INTO `rating` (`id`, `review`, `author`, `review_source`, `rating`, `title`, `product_name`, `reviewed_date`) VALUES
	(4394, 'I love using Amazon Echo Dot, but have one small issue, I have just recently purchased a Samsung tab s3 and I could set AED to my tablet but the issue is that I can\'t seem to be able to set up AED to my Samsung S7, if possible I would an answer to this... thank you!!', 'Paul Tribe', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4395, 'This app isn\'t perfect', 'Larry Smith', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4396, 'This app is either badly coded or has very poor server support.  Nearly every time I launch it, there is a very long - 5-10 min- wait before I can access it\'s functions.  This has been a problem for over 1 year yet it has not improved in response time. I have &gt;13kbps downlink and &gt;3kbps uplink speed - not great but enough to stream movies etc without hiccup.  I wiped my android phone to factory settings, reinstalled the app, and no improvement.  This app is the poorest face of Amazon I have ever interacted with.', 'Bryan Carson', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4397, 'Latest update has forced the calling and messaging feature. Can\'t access anything except the homepage unless I sign up to it. Really poor, this has in effect rendered Alexa useless to me now as I can\'t make any changes to my device and refuse to agree to the terms of the calling feature. WELL DONE! Will now try and get a refund for this nonsense.', 'Michael Ford', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4398, 'Can\'t us it on Android. It has been downloading for a full day and still nothing! App is installed but nothing else due to the app not getting settings or info from server?????', 'Edward mosher', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4399, 'If I could link it to my fly lady cleaning zones life would be grand!!', 'Daphne Nutter', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4400, 'Complete pain in the ass to setup does everything your phone does complete waste of f****** money', 'Ben Dover', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4401, 'Can\'t connect to me Samsung s7', 'Dominic Tessier', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4402, '3 Dots and Echo Show for Christmas!  Absolutely love it!', 'Sheri Smith', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4403, 'No account help from customer service at all', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4404, 'Do you guys plan on fixing this app any time soon? It would be nice to get the full use out of your product.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4405, 'Pure batter killer app.. today it drained out my new phone until I realized it\'s this app eating up all the battery.', 'Sameer Nafdey', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4406, 'Not getting the conversation button', 'Tammy Lockridge', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4407, 'App is clunky and slow at best. Words don\'t have the negative depth to describe the app itself. Setting up a simple Alexa echo has taken days with no progress because of how much the app freezes. Unfortunately mandatory.  Wouldn\'t imagine tech giant Amazon to has such a disgraceful app for its smart home interface. Never given out such a low score, especially for a company I\'m notoriously appreciative and forgiving toward.', 'John Cravey', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4408, 'How about a way customize commands including skills  i.e. \'alexa, ask roomba to start cleaning\'...Could be be customized to \'alexa, start cleaning\'.   Or, \'alexa, tell vivint to lock my doors\'  could be sumplified to. \'Alexa, lock my doors\'.  Also, a datatable showing commands and customizations of commands.', 'Troy Bowman', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4409, 'Awesome', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
