	(4412, 'App won\'t even let me open it. It says I have to update chrome but there is no update. Really irritating and such a let down', 'Hannah Lorraine', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4413, 'The app not working for me', 'Joyce Jeff', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4414, 'It would be nice if it excepted Canadian address not happy', 'Mark Brokenshire', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4415, 'Love it', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4416, 'I\'ve owned my tap for a year now and was really excited for the launch of Alexa in Canada. I try to set up my tap with Alexa, following all the instructions but always get stuck bring asked to manually connect to my tap. My tap gives the prompt that I\'m connected but nothing changes in the Alexa app. Something is not working and I am very disappointed after waiting so long.', 'Stephen Wen', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4417, 'It do sent work', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4418, 'I hate it !!dosent play music you have to pay', 'melissa caro', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4419, 'Love it!!', 'Enrika Johnson', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4420, 'Super easy to use if you have good WiFi and actually know how to use technology and aren\'t an old fart complaining because you can\'t figure it out. It\'s nothing more than a tablet without a screen but i love it. It\'s like a tablet for your mind if you learn it, use it enough, and train it and it can really fit seamlessly into your life. Being able to walk into my house and play a song i wish i had heard on the radio just by saying hey Alexa play "whatever" or being able to ask her to continue my sports talk show when i walk in is such a simple feature but so cool. It\'s nice to not have to find a new device when i walk in to reconnect everything i was listening to. The Echo Dot solves all those problems and there price is great. Highly recommended for anyone especially people who dont think they can use  something new like this. But it is so user friendly for all ages. 10/10', 'Matt Eubanks', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4421, 'App won\'t open on Android phone.  I have cleared the cache and uninstalled and reinstalled many times.  It just stops working.  So disappointed.', 'Laura Rud', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-28 00:00:00'),
	(4422, 'Works great with the Alexa Dot', 'Deborah Cieslewski', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-29 00:00:00'),
	(4423, 'Not working for me. Huge delay in sending code to link up phone', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-29 00:00:00'),
	(4424, 'does not work at all.', 'david jackson', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-29 00:00:00'),
	(4425, 'Its okay just a little improvment with samsung', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-29 00:00:00'),
	(4426, 'Nice app. Alexa is awesome. But I can not make calls through it. Tell me how to make calls or when I will be able to make calls through Alexa? Again Alexa can\'t play YouTube also she can\'t recognize different voices . Can I do above mentioned things in future? Could we ever store different profiles like Google Home?', 'surendra goyar', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-29 00:00:00'),
	(4427, 'Rick and morty all jessica scenes in the world of music and music and music and music and music and music and music and music and music', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-29 00:00:00'),
	(4428, 'Have used this app across multiple different devices and I always run into many issues most notably with alarms not setting. The app also crashes on my s8 while it is the app running. I expect much better from Amazon. Have had this app since the second month it was out and visually it\'s much better however the functionality is still sub par.', 'Jeremy Schnee', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-29 00:00:00'),
