	(4451, 'If you enable the calling and messaging feature (which gives them access to your full contact list), you cannot delete this yourself. The only way to deactivate this is to call customer service and get them to. Very sketchy Amazon.', 'David H', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-29 00:00:00'),
	(4452, 'I don\'t know why there are so many bad reviews, the echo dot works perfectly and so does the app. The only thing I have an issue with is that Google home responds to many more phrases than Alexa knows, especially when asking questions.', 'Luke Lenci', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-29 00:00:00'),
	(4453, 'Need more Canadian oriented skills! Give me skills!', 'Tyler Weber', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-29 00:00:00'),
