	(4455, 'Keeps duplicating my smart home devices', 'xXBadness185Xx', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-29 00:00:00'),
	(4456, 'This app is garbage and it just keeps getting worse, how can Amazon put so much effort into Alexa and not bother to make a decent app. App hangs up, UI is horrible and lacks key features. Updating wifi settings is a nightmare... Honestly if they don\'t pull it together Google home may be in my future', 'Nicholas Damon', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-29 00:00:00'),
	(4457, 'I can no longer control my devices from the app on my phone when playing music or podcasts, such as skipping tracks, controlling the volume, or pausing and stopping items that are playing. This has been the case for about 2 months now. Is anyone else experiencing this?', 'trayvious wilson', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-29 00:00:00'),
