	(4482, 'Trash app. Takes over a minute to open up now on my s7. Volume control of the echo no longer seems to work either.  Most of the Alexa app things are absolute turd. Only useful for music and news/weather..', 'Andrew Rossiter', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-30 00:00:00'),
	(4483, 'good, has to watch how you phrase things when asking her for information. I get a lot of I can\'t answer that.', 'Charles Gutelius', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-30 00:00:00'),
