	(4508, 'Can\'t even log on. App freezes before I\'m able to log in. U changed password twice. Tried different wifi. I will never buy another Amazon product.', 'Dave Peck', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-30 00:00:00'),
