	(4510, 'Needs more music service integrations.', 'Adrian Scarlett', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-30 00:00:00'),
	(4511, 'App works fine, but I feel like it\'s a system failure every time I have to use it. I want to do everything via the Alexa interface itself and never see the app.', 'Julie Wright', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-30 00:00:00'),
	(4512, 'Where\'s Your Voice in the UK, the US has had it for 2 months now. Not even getting to the fact Google home has been able to distinguish voices for over a year 😑', 'Antony Maina', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-30 00:00:00'),
	(4513, 'How is it possible?  How is it possible that Amazon, one of the biggest companies in the world have such terrible Apps.  Sure they work, but don\'t come close to the modern-day applications.  This Alexa app is good in principle but in practice, it\'s laggy and has a very dates feels.  The only app Amazon succeeds with, in my experience is the Audible App. Please let THAT team build the apps Amazon!', 'Finn Barnaby', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-30 00:00:00'),
	(4514, 'When dropping in from one Alexa device within our household  to another Alexa device within our household I am connected to the wrong device within our household. I am connected properly to the right device when using the app but device to device within our household simply doesn\'t work I am connected to the wrong device.', 'Stephen Wilmes', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-30 00:00:00'),
	(4515, 'Initial set up was tricky. When I got it connected and read all the info with a few visits to YouTube, I was able to make it work just fine. Pretty neat...😎👍', 'Joe Shaw', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-30 00:00:00'),
	(4516, 'Slow', 'Darren Johnstone', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-30 00:00:00'),
