	(4519, 'I have the app and Alexa on my smart thermostat, which doesn\'t support messaging. Someone sent a message a couple days ago and there is literally no way to clear the message. It keeps going off on the thermostat now with a notification every 5 minutes and it\'s super irritating', 'Haley Williams', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-30 00:00:00'),
	(4520, 'Was able to at least lock my front door before last update now alexa says my front door lock doesn\'t support that', 'Jared Woofter', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-30 00:00:00'),
	(4521, 'I\'ve used my Dot and Echo for several months now and rarely have to use the App as everything is working smoothly. I admit that the App, on my Samsung devices, could do with some improvement. My son uses the latest Echo with his iphone and was able to set up all the usual functions easily. He can control and monitor his heating system. I was delighted to find we could contact each other directly Echo to Echo. This device gets better all the time.', 'Michael Hutchinson', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-30 00:00:00'),
	(4522, 'Love it', 'Mike Wegrzyn', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-30 00:00:00'),
