	(4538, 'bekar', 'Akshay Thakur', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-30 00:00:00'),
	(4539, 'I have had my Alexa since Day 1. She has been a work in progress,  but she has never disappointed me! Speech is getting better and games are fun If you are a prime member,  then you will love her more as she lulls you to sleep with any song you want!', 'Rebecca West', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-31 00:00:00'),
	(4540, 'Amazon needs to put at least another year of research and development into this product, and application to even remotely make them useful. Worthless just worthless.', 'bill boyer', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-31 00:00:00'),
	(4541, 'I\'m not using the app much except to set up the devices, group them, and revisit my shopping list in the supermarket.  One thing that would be very useful however would be to allow devices to be placed in more than one group for music playback. I have a group called everywhere that has all devices in it, but I\'d also like to create a group called upstairs, and one called downstairs, to play music on just those devices. Sadly it appears I can\'t do that.  I\'ve no smart devices yet... but I hope this apparent restriction is not the similar for grouping those.', 'Steve Fulcher', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-31 00:00:00'),
	(4542, 'I like this app! It\'s very nice but you should add the tab \'Voice Training\' in the uk I want to try this really bad but otherwise really good.', 'PhantomPandaYT', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-31 00:00:00'),
	(4543, 'Can\'t make calls without giving Amazon access to ALL your contacts. Then, ANYONE with your phone number can call you through the device in your home and the app on your phone.', 'Jack Swann', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-31 00:00:00'),
