	(4545, 'Needs a language selection option. My phone is in English, but my account is in Japanese. The app is mainly in English. I want it in Japanese but I don\'t want to have to change my phone language to Japanese as well though. It\'s ridiculous that you can\'t change app language.', 'Chris Collingwood', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-31 00:00:00'),
