	(4550, 'Still needs more work. I got the time for it to get better. Worked day one out of the box, setting the device up was not a problem very quick. I wish that in settings I could set all of the information to Canadian setting. Also the voice is not a Canadian accent it\'s just a female robot voice. Just smooth out the dialogue transmission soon maybe in a January update or something.', 'Jason wisdom', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-31 00:00:00'),
