	(4554, 'I love it', 'DAVID BELLIDO', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, 'Echo', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-31 00:00:00'),
	(4555, 'I thought Amazon had smart people working for them - apparently no longer the case. They have no idea how to write setup instructions and  it won\'t setup to a telephone no already linked to an Amazon account - tells you to skip and call customer service but no clue as to the tell no.  Instructions talk about a "card" and a button to remove card but no clue as to what card they are talking about. Hopefully Google Home is more intelligent  I will discard my Echo Plus and I highly recommend you to not buy Echo Plus - complete waste of time and money.', 'Rick Bowman', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2017-12-31 00:00:00'),
