	(4687, 'This app has a long way to go. It is very clumsy and will randomly select things when scrolling. I am surprised that the company said "yeah, this works great lets go with this version."', 'Brent Cotterman', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-04 00:00:00'),
