	(4692, 'After the update everything went wrong. My app doesn\'t load.  I have to delete the app then it only works once. ****Update: The app works great now. Sometimes it has some loading issues but I am not sure that isn\'t just the internet connection.', 'Jenni Henry', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-04 00:00:00'),
