	(4698, 'It\'s a convenient device to have in the apartment and the quality of sound is pretty good. App freezes far too often, which I don\'t have this issue with any other apps I have on my phone. For music, the app does not display the full title of a song, such as classical music and movie scores.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-05 00:00:00'),
