	(4811, 'I can\'t connect Spotify Premium. The option is there but it\'s not able to be clicked! Searched the web and no solutions offered. A real shame as Alexa works really well with Amazon music BUT I want to use spotify as that is what I pay for!! Please HELP', 'Scott Gmail', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-10 00:00:00'),
	(4812, 'Tried to set up a account nothing but fails. Sorry wrong pw, then sorry can\'t connect, I\'m not wasting time to call customer service. Echo dot in garbage, elexa app not worth the hassle.', 'craig strom', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-10 00:00:00'),
	(4813, 'Alexa\'s functions are always improving (after all, she\'s only a few years old) and I absolutely love the convenience she\'s added to my life; however, I\'m surprised to see that this app is still struggling with some basic functionality issues (for example: the inability to see the text I\'m entering whenever I provide feedback or give a review for a given skill, unless the text window I\'m typing in is completely within the top portion of the screen--while all other apps adjust the window, as needed, to accommodate the keyboard pop-up, this app doesn\'t even allow you to scroll it up manually while the keyboard is present).  All in all, even though the app looks fine and accomplished it\'s overall functions without too many problems, it simply lacks the functional polish that I would expect from from an international giant like Amazon.', 'Troy Deitrick', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-10 00:00:00'),
