	(4831, 'Missing basic features like being able to set alarms without using my echo.  Really? Hoping an update will fix this ASAP.', 'Auto Sri', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-11 00:00:00'),
	(4832, 'Doesn\'t wait for command and doesn\'t respond while music is playing and it\'s just a "plastic box" if you\'re not connected to wifi... No offline commands.', 'Sanath Gowda', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-11 00:00:00'),
	(4833, 'No where near as easy to use as Google Assistant / Home apps... No material design for Android... No native option to open Alexa, whereas Google Assistant just hold the home button... Big thing is I don\'t need to buy hardware with Google for it to work (just use your phone if you want, don\'t buy any speakers), Amazon are really trying to push you spending money on Echo devices. Also Google Assistant is far far more natural in understanding what you are saying, Alexa requires very precise commands and doesn\'t always get them right, and I hate the excuse people are saying that "you have to make your own \'skills\'", no I really shouldn\'t need too! This should have machine learning and just understand me however I say it! Google does that perfectly by comparison... And one final thing, I can access, control and delete all my user data with Google, Amazon on the other hand - nothing, and yet Google is apparently the "bad boy" for user data mining!... Bottom line Google is simply the cheapest and highest performing option, and I\'ve now tested both. Sorry Amazon.', 'Robert Farr', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-12 00:00:00'),
	(4834, 'Sirius XM, account has to be linked everyday.  Why did this change.  Please fix!!!', 'Thomas Johns', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-12 00:00:00'),
