	(4837, 'Its quite sloooow!! and looks dated.  Fire stick was launched long back India, yet Echo integration with Firestick is not available in India like in other countries?. Text editing in the alexa app is terrible, cannot select or move the cursor. When are you fixing these issues.', 'Sachin TP', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-12 00:00:00'),
