	(4852, 'Fire everyone involved with working on this app! It has not worked for me for over 6 months. I have tried everything. I have downloaded older versions and I have tried the most up-to-date versions. All end up doing the same thing in the long run, which is work for one day then the next day all I get is a white screen with the home button and music button on the bottom but I cannot do anything with it. It\'s strange that it works for one day after he eats update. But that tells me it more than likely has nothing to do with my phone which is the latest Samsung Galaxy 8. There is also nothing wrong with my network I have reset everything I have problems with nothing but this app. I\'m going to try the Google mini. If that works will I will not be turning back to this product ever again. I have an echo dot which by itself is a fine piece of equipment, it\'s the app that needs to be thrown out. It\'s 3.5 rating reflects this.', 'na na', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-12 00:00:00'),
