	(4918, 'Alexa enabled groups don\'t work, there is no access to voice functions in the app and devices that are deleted return even if the account is disabled. I also find having only one fixed location for traffic updates and travel times poor, at the very least allow multiple preset trips. The worst issue is the way that the we keep being told about Alexa enabled groups and not having to specify device names but when you call support because it doesn\'t work they nothing about it.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-15 00:00:00'),
