	(4926, 'Amazing work from Amazon 😃😃😃', 'Dheeraj Pareek', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-15 00:00:00'),
	(4927, 'The app is garbage! It just sits there with three dots on the screen and I can\'t connect to the echo.  I have deleted the app and reinstalled it 3 times and still nothing.  I have an S7, not some ancient phone.', 'Miguel Contreras', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-15 00:00:00'),
	(4928, 'I do love my Alexa. But it seemed like this app is constantly being updated with the same things that it says it\'s fixing or updating the last 3 or 4 updates I\'ve gotten. All state that it\'s fixing smart home features but its exact  Same fix as its reporting reporting come on Amazon. Get with the picture', 'Curtis E Norris Jr', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-15 00:00:00'),
	(4929, 'Thank you for making more broadly available.', 'Jussi Palo', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-15 00:00:00'),
	(4930, 'To call family', 'Mary Abraham', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-15 00:00:00'),
	(4931, 'Updated today but still cant edit times for reminders!!!! HELLO DEVELOPERS!!!! YOU NEED TO FIX THE REMINDERS SECTION IN THE APP. When setting a reminder on the android app there is no way to pick a time. It says either "clear" or "cancel" any ideas?', 'Jeff', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-15 00:00:00'),
	(4932, 'Not really a problem with the app but more my alexa and it playing music with Spotify, I will ask it to play a certain album in Spotify that I have and it will play something different, and also one of my radio stations on tunein radio it won\'t play so have given up on it a bit now.', 'Janet Dinsdale', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-15 00:00:00'),
	(4933, 'Excellent', 'asif riyaz', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-15 00:00:00'),
	(4934, 'App is good, does the job without a fuss however it gets a 1 star from me because there\'s no option to control Fire TV devices however this has been available in America since last year.', 'sammy laver', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-16 00:00:00'),
	(4935, 'It good but Google as the edge', 'Stephen Thornton', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-16 00:00:00'),
	(4936, 'For a few updates my Lifx scenes have not been working, so I have had to create Routines to run them. Get the basics right first and stop screwing up Alexa!', 'Mark Edward Maciel', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-16 00:00:00'),
	(4937, 'The device itself is good.  The is horrible.  App design (looks) are too simplified (politely saying childish).  The names of functions is not intuitive but worse is the nested options.  You need to know what THEY call it and WHERE it is burried.  No support to speak to. You can not even ask the device to help you', 'Daniel Nazzaro', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-16 00:00:00'),
	(4938, 'My smart home lights quit working after this update. Horrible', 'Aaron Knoll', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-16 00:00:00');
INSERT INTO `rating` (`id`, `review`, `author`, `review_source`, `rating`, `title`, `product_name`, `reviewed_date`) VALUES
	(4939, 'Great app, but no app is perfect.  I know the folks at Amazon are working overtime to make this better and that is much appreciated. The only flaw that I have noticed isn\'t really a flaw, but it could use some work. Making the Integrations to other apps to control other devices smoother would be the focus of why I only gave it 4 stars. Everything else is superb.', 'B L', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-16 00:00:00'),
	(4940, 'Until Amazon addresses the ridiculous geographic restrictions for skills outside of the US this is as high a rating as it deserves.', 'Dion Dubé', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-16 00:00:00'),
	(4941, 'Will not work. Signed out now can\'t sign back in. Said password wrong got new password still can\'t sign in did that four times. Uninstalled and reinstalled 4 times. Still won\'t work. Have been trying to set it up for two days The Alexa dot is a piece of garbage.', 'Paul Thoensen', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-16 00:00:00'),
