	(4963, 'Can you customise the wake word', 'Shadow Hunter 3221', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-17 00:00:00'),
	(4964, 'Love it  Nice', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-17 00:00:00'),
	(4965, 'Grate', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-17 00:00:00'),
	(4966, 'Hardware gets 5* but app is stuck in 2010. The app is really poor and even basic stuff like searching for local radio can be painful as typeahead gets in a way. Also setting my Geo location didn\'t help with local suggestion. Not sure what is the point of setting it up. Surely you can do better Amazon. As I yes. I love the headwear, but hate using the app. Luckily that\'s not too often.', 'Tomas Kuzma', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-17 00:00:00'),
	(4967, 'Good times for everyone.', 'Jeremy Evanson', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-17 00:00:00'),
	(4968, 'Good app if you don\'t mind waiting an eternity for it to load', 'Serge M', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-17 00:00:00'),
	(4969, 'Love it', 'Cassie Fisher', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-17 00:00:00'),
	(4970, '"Play new age radio on Pandora." "Getting your ambient station--" Uh...no. There are clearly two stations on there, Ambient and New Age. To play the new age I have to go through this app, so it doesn\'t work properly.', 'Derek Larios', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-17 00:00:00'),
	(4971, 'Even after am update I can\'t see "your voice" on the settings on this Canada Amazon Alexa app. Can you please make it available. Thanks.', 'Suleiman Orotta', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-17 00:00:00'),
	(4972, 'Keeps saying Error Code 505', 'Maria Vargas', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-17 00:00:00'),
