	(4974, 'I live in canada and everything in my house that is Smart alexa does not have a skill for example sonos, neato robotics, b-hyve and much more.', 'mike muscat', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-17 00:00:00'),
