	(4976, 'The best feature in my eyes is the grocery list. The worst feature is the grocery list. I can add items with my voice easy, very convenient, but can\'t remove items that way. Then when I\'m at the store it takes forever to load the list and then if my screen locks it doesn\'t bring me back to the list so it has to load again. Stuck in the ailes. Come on.', 'David Yang', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-17 00:00:00'),
