	(4999, 'Alexa does an excellent job recognizing commands. The iot folks should add more features.', 'Michael Grech', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-18 00:00:00'),
	(5000, 'Used to work.  Android 6 on Galaxy tab S. App crashes at login screen. Can\'t get past it.', 'bajagadget', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-18 00:00:00'),
	(5001, 'This brighten up my day but you have to buy smart bulbs in order to tell Alexa to turn on your lights ice and buy smart plugs to tell Alexa to turn on your stuff too much money', 'Racing King360', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-18 00:00:00'),
	(5002, 'I loved this app.  Paid for ad free.  It thanked me by putting a full page ad right after my unlock screen any time I rebooted.  Easy to close full screen ad with X.  But who is to say it did not place a tracker on my phone.  Grrr.   I deleted it and ad went away. Waste of my money!!  But the APP is kewl.', 'Sherri Anders', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-18 00:00:00'),
	(5003, 'Every question I ask Alexa or skills on my echo dot she can\'t do. The app always says it\'s offline. It\'s not. I try to reconnect or do a new setup and it just won\'t. The app sucks. And Alexa doesn\'t do what I need done. I had her set alarms and they were going off at 3am waking me 5hrs before I was supposed to hear alarm. Just updated app and still can\'t get Alexa to sync with any apps so I can use my dot efficiently.', 'Tabitha ConnellyGeorge', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-18 00:00:00'),
	(5004, 'It wouldn\'t connect, it was constantly loading and I couldn\'t do anything with the app.', 'Isabella Samson', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-18 00:00:00'),
	(5005, 'I think this thing night help', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-18 00:00:00'),
	(5006, 'Won\'t do anything at all. I want sports updates, but literally everything I press or say goes back to asking for my mobile number so people can call me via Alexa. I don\'t want this, but the skip option just results in being asked again in 30 seconds. Total doorstop.', 'Rose Rodent', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-19 00:00:00'),
	(5007, 'The good: Works as advertised.  Smart home feature 5 stars. The bad: Started getting Amazon full page ads popping up at random times on my android phone in late December.  Uninstalled the app they stopped...disapointed', 'John Haney', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-19 00:00:00'),
	(5008, 'If your just looking for a simple task this may not be yo thang but if ur gonna put in the work it\'s da bomb', 'itsyaboy Keegan', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-19 00:00:00'),
	(5009, 'I want talk to family.', 'Mary Abraham', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-19 00:00:00'),
	(5010, 'Now if this app could be a so called hybrid between the other smart devices with what it can already do that be awesome but lately the app crashes after getting into any other categories or even the settings. Wish it wouldn’t happen. And wish it would be noted and worked on immediately.', 'Bassin guy', 'iTunes', 4, 'Apps really good but', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-19 14:19:40'),
	(5011, 'Please optimize for iPhone X', 'ScottPowers', 'iTunes', 3, 'iPhone X', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-19 14:46:04');
INSERT INTO `rating` (`id`, `review`, `author`, `review_source`, `rating`, `title`, `product_name`, `reviewed_date`) VALUES
	(5012, 'Stuck on allow permission. Nothing loads', 'Celine3005', 'iTunes', 1, 'Won’t open.', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-19 14:54:09'),
	(5013, 'I bet Amazon would sell more Alexa enabled devices if they had a decent app. Their IT department is absolutely brilliant when it comes to the Amazon website (as well as the back end) but it seems that they\'ve put rookies to work developing the Alexa app. How about a real search function, for instance? With Sonos you can search across all of the streaming services in your account. Come on Bezos, you\'ve got the money to invest to develope a much better app. Please improve this light weight!', 'Average Joe312', 'iTunes', 2, 'Mediocrity reigns supreme', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-19 19:41:07'),
	(5014, 'Please', 'Spider Man !!!', 'iTunes', 2, 'Optimize your app for iPhone X', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-19 22:18:52'),
	(5015, 'So frustrating! Stupid app keeps asking for permission to upload my phone contacts and when I try to click later it freezes on that screen. I close the app all the way out reopen it, still frozen on that screen. I have deleted and reinstalled the app 5 times. I finally caved and hit allow so it would just move on. Nope. Froze again anyway.', 'Fenner.Fam', 'iTunes', 1, 'I don’t want my contacts uploaded!!!', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-19 22:50:48'),
	(5016, 'After newest update yesterday the first thing that comes in when you open the app is to allow permissions. It won’t let you press later or allow and is frozen on that screen. It will let you read the FAQ section but will return you to the original permissions screen where it continues to stay frozen.', 'DoodleStick', 'iTunes', 1, 'Won’t let me in', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-19 23:06:43'),
	(5017, 'Wasted past 2 hours trying to set up my brand new Alexa. The app is incredibly slow and will not connect with my wi-fi. Very disappointing.', 'Flanorama', 'iTunes', 1, 'Horrible app. I regret getting an Echo', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-19 23:13:52'),
	(5018, 'I give 5 stars because I love my Alexa devices, but feel the "Routines" feature has a lot of room for growth.  So far, I\'ve been happy with what it can do and have had a little fun playing with it.  I like walking into my office in the morning and saying "Alexa, time to get to work" and having all my lights turn on, followed by news and sports updates.  \n\nAdmittedly, my gripe comes from the app\'s lack of imagination. I envision being able to change the color/dimming of the lighting, and having the option to trigger a particular song/artist/genre of music to begin playing.  My sick, twisted mind hypothesized a scenario where I say "Alexa, it\'s business time" and the lights dim, change color, and Flight of the Concords starts playing.  Just seems like it could be a lot of fun!', 'rdrnr7551', 'iTunes', 5, 'Love it, but it has room to grow.', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-20 01:02:28'),
	(5019, 'Useless in my phone for now...hope they fix it.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-19 00:00:00'),
	(5020, 'Works fine', 'Bart Brady Ciampa', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-19 00:00:00'),
	(5021, 'Does not work at all on my galaxy s7', 'brandon robinson', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-19 00:00:00'),
	(5022, 'I love using Alexa but the app is so slow and crashes constantly. It\'s hard to use it for your shopping lists as intended. When you want to do anything in the app give yourself a 5-10 second delay every thing you click on. I hope the Amazon team reads this and fixes this terrible app experience', 'Jennifer Seigal', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-19 00:00:00'),
