	(5052, 'I just got an Alexa as a gift and tried to set it up. I downloaded the app and signed in and now it is a blank white screen. I have tried closing and opening the app many times but it does not work.', 'emitortiz', 'iTunes', 1, 'Not working', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-20 15:22:24'),
	(5053, 'It won’t display what is playing anymore, nor can volume be adjusted. It often plays one song from Pandora and abruptly stops playing the station. Please improve this app! As it is, it has become useless.', 'Maretmuse', 'iTunes', 1, 'App keeps getting worse', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-20 17:54:47'),
	(5054, 'When I\'m at the store or at a coffeehouse, Lists will not open even thought I am connected to the internet with full bars. Alexa is great at home, but when I try to use the app on my iPad to view my Lists, Alexa is useless.', 'Will they ever get it right?', 'iTunes', 1, 'LIsts? --- Forget about it', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-20 20:38:40'),
	(5055, 'App is slow and keeps crashing. Cannot get my echo plus back online and it’s not remembering my network. Crashes every time I open the settings tab.', 'Flush beats a pair ', 'iTunes', 2, 'Crash', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-20 23:02:17'),
	(5056, 'I have ewe-Link automation devices in all my house, when I use the ewe- Link app to control them it is easy and fast but when I use Alexa (Amazon Alexa with echo Dot) Alexa understands the command and send it from Amazon-Alexa’s Cloud to ewe’s Cloud (accounts previously linked accordingly) sometimes Alexa respond: The server is not responding, after that sometimes it takes more than 3 minutes to turn on or turn off a device or sometimes it does not do anything to complete the action.\nIn the other side, sometimes (not very frequent) I have very good experiences (fast response with Alexa and ewe-Link clouds) and I can do whatever I want smoothly with no delays, that makes me believe it is a communication problem between clouds.\nWe hope developers take action to fix this issue.\nAlso I want to say with Spotify it works very well always so far.', 'artuuroo', 'iTunes', 1, 'Slow communication with other Clouds', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-20 23:18:45'),
	(5057, 'Terrible. Glitchy, crashes often, drop in functionality doesn’t work, can’t connect to Amazon Music.', 'FMD31', 'iTunes', 1, 'Worthless', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-21 00:04:23'),
	(5058, 'Trouble constantly syncing with WiFi and it does not just use blue tooth anywhere! You must have a WiFi connection Bluetooth is useless!!! I’ve tried using this with the Bose I purchased most of the time that doesn’t even work! WHAT A WASTE OF MY TIME AND MONEY!!! This whole thing is so restrictive that I just don’t even use it “AFTER SPENDING SO MUCH” this has to be corrected! I want a total refund!!! Very Seriously! What a hassle! What a hassle to have to return it because it’s useless!', '"L")', 'iTunes', 1, 'Syncing anything!?!', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-21 06:22:25'),
	(5059, 'Too clunky. If I can get it open it feezes. However, I love my Echo!', 'Linda Banks', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-20 00:00:00'),
	(5060, 'I wish I didn\'t include Internet thanks', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-20 00:00:00'),
