	(5062, 'Work area is very small. it cant ordr pizza, cnt change booking, cant cancell booking, cant play folk song punjabi song cant play bhakti sangeet. Data at its server is not updated till now. Thumbs up to team need to expand area,', 'rajeev bhatia', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-20 00:00:00'),
