	(5125, 'Aaaargh!!! What on EARTH made Amazon pick BING as the *only* search engine this app will use. I have literally ZERO trust in bing and use the world\'s leading search engine every time, not that noddy piece of nonsense. Please at least LET ME CHOOSE Google!!! So search is 100% useless until Amazon and Google make it up and behave like adults again.  Also, since some aspects are built-in, such as shopping lists, why not have a widget or app to let me add to it and tick items off - look at Google Keep if you\'re not sure.', 'Colin Main', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-22 00:00:00'),
