	(5207, 'Player no longer showing books or music currently playing, even when initiated from the app. Means I can\'t control volume or pause what is playing from the app or control multiple Echo devices without being in the room.', 'Erica Brown', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5208, 'Life Changing Functionality With The New Alexa Button...Make A Widget!', 'Joseph Giardina', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5209, 'Good for setup. But echo dot constantly drops prime music connections', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5210, 'Most recent update makes the app useless.  App opens, freezes and closes.', 'Mel0149', 'iTunes', 1, 'Most recent Jan 2018 update', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 10:04:42'),
	(5211, 'At some point it was working (I configured my Echo Dot with this app), but after some of the more recent iOS and/or App updates I am getting Connection Timeout. I called Amazon’s tech support and they don’t know what it is, but apparently I am not the only one with the issue. I am on an iPhone X with the latest iOS.', 'NoisyDude', 'iTunes', 1, 'Connection Timeout', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 10:29:05'),
	(5212, 'Come on Amazon much smaller companies already support iPhone X. Time to step it up', 'Marhaba69', 'iTunes', 2, 'Time to support iPhone X', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 13:00:21'),
	(5213, 'UI design is just as important as functionality. The iPhone X has been out long enough that this app should support its screen, but it doesn’t. Please update for iPhone X screen!', 'macpr088', 'iTunes', 1, 'Still no iPhone X support', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 13:01:36'),
	(5214, 'I can no longer see the music player on the app at all. Those screenshots look nothing like what the current “updated” app looks like on my devices. It’s exceedingly frustrating to not be able to adjust volume or change the song only through voice commands. Please fix this developers!', 'Megz713', 'iTunes', 2, 'App is glitchy', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 13:31:21'),
	(5215, 'Please make this app support the iPhone X', 'alecminichini', 'iTunes', 1, 'STILL WHY DOESNT THIS APP SUPPORT THE IPHONE X?', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 14:04:11'),
	(5216, 'It’s not Alexa. It is really an app for the device set up, but why can’t make Alexa available on the phone? Is it because Amazon wants people to buy more Echos? The app is confusing and it needs a redesign badly. Amazon needs to take note of this low review ratings.', 'JazHunt', 'iTunes', 1, 'It needs a redesign', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 14:54:07'),
	(5217, 'I only bought my 4 echos to use with multi room music, ever since they launched the feature for Spotify it’s never worked properly, half the time I try to use the feature only one or some of the echos will even play music the rest do nothing.', 'BearsIn3D', 'iTunes', 2, 'Spotify multi room music doesn’t work....still', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 16:01:15'),
	(5218, 'The app is blank every time I open it. Just top bar white screen.', 'Oliver Deez', 'iTunes', 1, 'App is blank', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 17:25:35'),
	(5219, 'Developers have to continually make modifications to justify their existence and employment.  In this case, they have turned an app that worked fine into one that does NOT work fine.  \nVery, very disappointing.\nI am deleting this app from my phone.', 'Ardant', 'iTunes', 1, 'Bad Idea', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 17:43:56'),
	(5220, 'Since I’ve installed this update, I cannot get the app to do anything but hope. After that I can do nothing.', 'Da_bears22', 'iTunes', 1, 'App doesn’t work', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 18:09:48');
INSERT INTO `rating` (`id`, `review`, `author`, `review_source`, `rating`, `title`, `product_name`, `reviewed_date`) VALUES
	(5221, 'this app is SO surprisingly bad. it takes a very long time to launch, even after i JUST had it open. highly unresponsive - i always have to try each button twice. the sections of the app are organized in such a counterintuitive way that even after using it a LOT i still can\'t seem to learn it. you can\'t even launch the app unless you are connected to the internet - why can\'t it just hold reminders etc in its memory until it finds a signal? every other app under the sun does. focus group this and LISTEN. whoever is running this should be doing soething else, app creation/design is not your thing.', 'Ron Lent', 'iTunes', 1, 'c\'mon guys!', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 20:08:10'),
	(5222, 'Routines are significantly more useful with Stringify added as a device. I’m happy this is supported again.\n\nHowever... it’s still a challenge to figure out how to set it up. There is nothing in the Alexa UI that helps you through the process. If you try something and it doesn’t work, there is no diagnostic help. This and other usability improvements are needed.\n\n—', 'SeriouslyDave', 'iTunes', 3, 'Stringify again supported in routines', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 22:04:34'),
	(5223, 'The only reason I have an Alexa is to use my iHome smart device plugs and now strangely those don’t work with Alexa anymore! I updated the app and still nothing. It also doesn’t know the answer to practically any question I ask. Really wish I had Google Home instead.', 'renn12m', 'iTunes', 1, 'Useless', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:18:51'),
	(5224, 'App opens but does not allow you to click anything. Worked decent until an update. I want to be able to use it to view new skills, lists, etc. disappointed', 'Wonderwags', 'iTunes', 1, 'Horrible', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 01:32:33'),
	(5225, 'App was updated yesterday (version2.2.1797.0) and will now not control any iHome devices or even find them on a discovery search. Alexa worked fine with the iHome devices until the update which was suppose to make iHome devices easier to use. Need to fix the update now.', 'Big D51', 'iTunes', 1, 'Updated App causing problems', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 01:45:37'),
	(5226, 'They had been many updates since the iPhone X has been out. This app still lack support. So, Many errors are still present due to the format or something else.', 'Thomas L Thomas', 'iTunes', 1, 'iPhone X no love', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 02:25:16'),
	(5227, 'I’d like to wake up to Spotify music, have a snooze option...basically more customization options...weather, traffic & smart home just doesn’t cut it', 'mikesterc', 'iTunes', 2, 'More Actions....', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 02:34:16'),
	(5228, 'please then ill change to 5', 'bobbybrown3142', 'iTunes', 3, 'iphone x support', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 02:49:41'),
	(5229, 'And that defeats the purpose of having an Alexa.\n\nAlso update your app for the iPhone 10 and stop with the javascript/electron bs.', 'SleepingInsomniac', 'iTunes', 1, 'Alexa always asks me to use the app...', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 03:01:51'),
	(5230, 'Amazon is forcing you to sign up for a voice calling service you may not want otherwise it is blocking you from using the other parts of the app', 'Toro001', 'iTunes', 1, 'Terrible', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 03:03:44'),
	(5231, 'If you have to many alarms pre set the app will continually crash when you go to the alarm/timer section .', 'Winwin2442', 'iTunes', 1, 'App keeps crashing', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 06:52:02'),
	(5232, 'The fact that i cant type a search for specific songs from this app is so frustrating? If i have the music up loud alexa cant hear me telling her to play a different song id like to do it from my phone but you have to go through all the different playlist and genres to search for the song you want if you can even find it. This wouldnt yield only 2 stars if i used alexa for something other than music but thats literally all i use her for', 'countesspink', 'iTunes', 2, 'Weak', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 07:53:34'),
	(5233, 'Honestly a waste of time. Setting up music is a hassle. Don’t bother with this garbage app and use the PC version.', 'Babylp315', 'iTunes', 1, 'Don’t get', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 08:37:51'),
	(5234, 'Slow and painful to use.', 'Sarc 1942', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00');
INSERT INTO `rating` (`id`, `review`, `author`, `review_source`, `rating`, `title`, `product_name`, `reviewed_date`) VALUES
	(5235, '1/26/18 AGAIN AN UPDATE TODAY AND NO TIME REMINDERS ABLE TO BE EDITED STILL.  HELLO DEVELOPERS!!!! YOU NEED TO FIX THE REMINDERS SECTION IN THE APP. When setting a reminder on the android app there is no way to pick a time. It says either "clear" or "cancel" any ideas?', 'Jeff', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5236, 'Can not download app. Keep getting a 505 error code. After following the instructions on what might be causing the app not to download and then trying again download app i still have the same problem and same error message code. Any advice from any of you on how to download this app would be greatly appreciated.', 'Donnie Montgomery', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5237, 'It\'s great', 'Mike Miller', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5238, 'Can\'t seem to remove routine actions. Nor adjust my Nest temperature from routines.', 'Luke Addington', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5239, 'This app now weighs in at nearly 250Mb. I wish they offered a Alexa Light version to configure devices and not much else for my phone...  I have (1) Echo, (3) Echo Dots, (3) Amazon tablets of 7", 8", and 10", (1) 2016 AWD Ford Taurus which works in conjunction with the Ford+Alexa app on my phone - I don\'t think my phone needs to be a full blown Alexa device...', 'Timothy Christy', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5240, 'Christopher. Is aswome', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5241, 'need a alexa button on my home screen outside of the app', 'Mike Schoenherz', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5242, 'Needs work. When I view settings under devices there is one that says "This Device". I had to login to my Amazon account on my computer to see what it is - my Amazon Alexa app. But when I rename it, the name still shows up as "This Device" in the app. Very confusing!', 'Cat T.', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5243, 'I\'M REALLY getting sick of waiting for the ability to control my fire tv stick with my echo dot! USA market has had this for ages! At least I can control my chromecast with my google home! Google 1 - 0 Amazon', 'Steve G', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5244, 'It\'s. Cool', 'mary h', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5245, 'Still really not well thought out UX and non Amazon device integration is lousy experience. Still long way to go before decently mature product', 'arkley68', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5246, 'Finally, Amazon added control from the app to use like an Echo device. Guess they got tired of Google Home being more advanced quicker smh', 'Aris T', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5247, 'Love it', 'Sean Drane', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5248, 'Good', 'Shari Kojima', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5249, 'Alwsøme thing had', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5250, 'Where\'s the button?????? No button', 'Anand M', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5251, 'Lame', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5252, 'Why do I need Spotify premium account to play music on Amazon Echo? I can play music from Spotify on my Google Home and I have free account only.', 'milos milos', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-26 00:00:00'),
	(5253, 'Can\'t control fire tv like US can.  Not fair the Americans get all the good features.  Bring this to the uk please. I got a fire but want to get 3 more for my other tvs in the house to control with my echos but I won\'t get more until this option is available.  Please bring it here. Plus allow us to to replace Google assistant with Alexa in Android.', 'alan fletcher', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00');
INSERT INTO `rating` (`id`, `review`, `author`, `review_source`, `rating`, `title`, `product_name`, `reviewed_date`) VALUES
	(5254, 'I download this because i have amazon music and Android does not allow Amazon music to be the, "default music provider". I had hoped to replace, "ok Google play bla bla bla" with, "Alexa play song x!" In stead I must push a blue button which really defeats the idea of hands free. So my options are to by some ridiculous thing I have no need for or switch to an android supported default provider.  Basically the app is useless unless you get echo or whatever... at that point the device just leaches function from your phone... maybe I\'m wrong but looking at the horrid ratings on this app tells me Amazon is taking a wrong turn here, too bad, I actually liked their services.', 'William Kimball', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5255, 'Still we Indians have not got the Alexa calling features and many more... This is unfair we are paying all as other countries do than why we are not getting same features like them?', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5256, 'Terrible recent update. It used to be that only your contacts who have registered for Alexa calling and messaging will appear as contacts in your Alexa App.  Now you just get the whole long list of your contacts imported into the app and you have to search through the list for them.', 'James Bartlett', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5257, 'Good', 'Navith Perera', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5258, 'Their was no option for Amazon spot?', 'Hannah s', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5259, 'Fantastic', 'Kishin Awatramani', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5260, 'Have uninstall and reinstall every time just to make it work', 'Andy Stephen', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5261, 'Great been using dot for a year now with Alexa apk app. But now available in Ireland can access proper official app. Works great....well done Amazon my dot feels brand new....like it\'s been jazzed up', 'Ciaran O Dea', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5262, 'App performance need to improve and hang to much.', 'sujeet jaiswara', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5263, 'Most features are us only. Recommended not to buy/download. Your siri or Bixby voice is better', 'Jason English', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5264, 'App is ok but I wouldn\'t say user friendly. Layout is confusing. Considering how much you can do via the app, it is difficult to find what you\'re looking for. Please improve as this is an important app.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5265, 'All the good features are available on US .Why I have also purchased with money ,they have not provided free of cost in India .I want full features in India .', 'Jitesh Pandey', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5266, 'The fact that in Canada this doesn\'t even work on the Amazon made tablet I\'m typing on right now is sad.', 'Noah Lear', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5267, 'Yup', 'Kyle Keyte', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5268, 'App required with use of Echo devices. The recent update makes using the Echo Dot more convenient.  Echo Dot listens for the action word to respond to requests, but ambient noise often prevents Echo from hearing spoken requests. Strangely enough, until recently, the one thing missing from the Amazon Alexa app was...Alexa. With the addition of Alexa, Echo users no longer need to shout or quiet their environment. We can now issue voice commands to Echo via cellphone when necessary.', 'Rip Washington', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5269, 'Stay tuned for info.', 'Wild Life', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00');
INSERT INTO `rating` (`id`, `review`, `author`, `review_source`, `rating`, `title`, `product_name`, `reviewed_date`) VALUES
	(5270, 'I downloaded the app on my brand new Galaxy Note 8.  Once the app is opened it takes forever to load anything in it, if it even loads.  I\'ve uninstalled and reinstalled the app 4 times now with no improvement to the functionality of the app. Very frustrating.  I\'m currently using an older version of the app on my Amazon Fire tablet and I\'m hesitant to update that device with the new version for fear I won\'t be as to do anything in the app.  Currently the old app still works but many skills won\'t work without the new version. I\'m beyond disappointed.  What\'s the use of having the Echo if the app doesn\'t even work properly?', 'Kajayjay', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5271, 'Alexa didn\'t answer most questions asked.', 'Laura Blanchard', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5272, 'I can\'t get the Facebook link to work to log into my heart radio :( The app is not always easy to navigate :(', 'Jacqueline Thompson', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5273, 'I have 2 Dots and one Echo. I have 4 smart light lamps and a Firestick. They all work as promised, individually or grouped. Pretty simple to set up, fun to have “at my command (or request).” I enjoy exploring skills and options that are there or come with each new update. I highly recommend these devices.', 'RevGlennB', 'iTunes', 5, 'Echo, Dot, Alexa and all', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 11:44:43'),
	(5274, 'This last update was said to make adding and controlling iHome devices easier. Well now Alexa can’t find my ihome smartplugs and says there was a problem while my devices are working fine through their app. Please fix this', 'bryanvincent', 'iTunes', 3, 'IHome control update broke it', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 13:09:34'),
	(5275, 'Probably the worst app that has touched my phone. I’ve set up three devices and every time the app is glitchy and takes FOREVER to work. This time I’ve been trying to set up a new Echo for over TWO HOURS. It is NOT my internet connection - I check every time. STAY AWAY FROM AMAZON PRODUCTS.', 'Soconnell80', 'iTunes', 1, 'Horrible', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 13:41:40'),
	(5276, 'This app is very badly designed with almost no help features. It’s hard to figure out the most basic tasks and the online help is almost worthless. Come on Jeff, if you want the to be the Home hub if the future, make it more user friendly!', 'Puzzla dude', 'iTunes', 2, 'Badly Designed with Little Documentation', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 15:19:06'),
	(5277, 'The multi-room option of my music 1-doesn’t play on all the devices I originally set up and 2-can’t really be navigated to, when I tap the multi-room music button it goes into the smart home setup', 'GCarter', 'iTunes', 3, 'Multi room music', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 16:42:46'),
	(5278, 'Latest updates date claims to improve smart home functions, however, actually not.  Ihome plugs no longer function with Alexa. They’re working fine with Apple Home though!  Please ‘fix’ the update!', 'Jayjaynjake', 'iTunes', 1, 'No longer works with ihome plugs', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 17:11:26'),
	(5279, 'I’m out of town and my sister-in-law told me her Alexa app wouldn’t control her iHome products. I confidently told her there had been an update to the app yesterday. Then I went to my Alexa app to control my outlets. I can’t control my outlets either. The ‘bug fixes and performance enhancements’ made things worse! Very frustrating.', 'PonyGirl321', 'iTunes', 1, 'Alexa worse after 1/26/18 update', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 18:16:24'),
	(5280, 'This app is not working since update.  No skills, lists, not even help.  Totally useless!', 'Charlie4aid', 'iTunes', 1, 'App not working, blank', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 19:21:07'),
	(5281, 'Now all of a sudden after this update my smart plugs are non-responsive with the Alexa app. It works with my iHome app, so I know that it’s connected. What Alexa will not control the Plugs.', 'Cmplastic', 'iTunes', 1, 'Disconnect with smart plugs', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 20:15:57');
INSERT INTO `rating` (`id`, `review`, `author`, `review_source`, `rating`, `title`, `product_name`, `reviewed_date`) VALUES
	(5282, 'Alexa is great. The companion app is horrible.  It’s slow. It lack and user friendly interface. It’s slow. It tries to do too much as does nothing we’ll. It’s slow. If I’m at a grocery store with less than great cell service, the shopping list is almost useless - freezes, won’t delete item (why?!) so I have to continue to scroll through a long list (and the scrolling freezes). Please make an app worthy of pairing with Alexa.', 'sternbel', 'iTunes', 1, 'Slowest app I’ve ever seen', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 01:46:49'),
	(5283, 'The app seems to always work for me but it lacks the simplicity and frills like a customizable widget for smart home.', 'JMitchamo', 'iTunes', 2, 'It works with no frills', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 04:39:47'),
	(5284, 'Can you please make Alexa smarter please', 'picksapu', 'iTunes', 3, 'I.Q', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 05:09:09'),
	(5285, 'Anyone near the echo can retrieve the text messages on your cell phone via the echo without your permission. It’s not pw or pin protected and echo will read it aloud for all to hear.', 'betterjeff', 'iTunes', 1, 'Your privacy is gone', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 05:15:46'),
	(5286, 'Great app', 'Paul Ward', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5287, 'Bomb dizzle wizzle.', 'Steve Jarvis', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5288, 'I have the dot in the bathroom and echo in the livingroom.  I have them connected to each other, it\'s like having speakers everywhere and having control everwhere.  Love them.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5289, 'The new update makes it impossible to access my reminders via the app?? Every time you try to open reminders it takes you back to the home screen on the app.... Please fix as I use this daily. It won\'t even open the reminders from the recent \'cards\' please fix..!!!', 'sam watson', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5290, 'I realize my expectations were way too high.  It is essentially a voice recognition connected to a few features that seem selected and tuned for building revenue stream.  Unless you like the cool toy aspect, Id wait another year at least and I\'m not sure Amazon is necessarily the company that will be bringing it.  They seem good at using technology to build POS revenue stream, not developing technology.', 'Mark Lamb', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5291, 'Please add the option for the echo show to change the accent (BRITISH).  Its available only with the dot! That would make it perfect', 'Nalda Santana', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5292, 'drained 10% battery trying to open settings just endlessly spins', 'Steve Swartzlander', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5293, 'It works great, sometimes it has issues when I want to type in the app, otherwise I love it and I love Alexa', 'Glen Wooldridge', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5294, 'Still learning after 6 months', 'John Allen', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5295, 'Apparently it does not work on a brand new Motorola E4. Just get the 3 blue dots rolling on the home screen. App never loads cards or controls. Works on every other device in the house. Sucks.', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5296, 'Since last update, freezes and closes. Useless.', 'Nadezhda Hudzik', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5297, 'Its Simply Amazing', 'scott warnick', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00'),
	(5298, 'Playback of commands heard by Alexa is broken. Often plays two or three times at once with the sound clip overlaid. Otherwise great app', 'Sydney Park', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-27 00:00:00');
INSERT INTO `rating` (`id`, `review`, `author`, `review_source`, `rating`, `title`, `product_name`, `reviewed_date`) VALUES
	(5299, 'Getting there could be better. I like that I can remotely do things from my phone to my echo, however unless it\'s an action you recently done and is on the history tab I cannot find how you\'d open it without.  Also it\'d be nice if I could rename the Bluetooth devices connected rather than need my app to change i.e. I have a audio bridge dongle for my amp called a technika BT1305 which requires me to ask for it by name to connect, it\'d be easier to ask Alexa connect to amp or connect to bedroom speaker.  Other than that love it', 'Adam Grant', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5300, 'It is very slow...Even when network and data speed is good', 'lokesh patel', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5301, 'Amazing', 'Abhishek Kolapalli', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5302, 'Totally utter rubbish.  Can\'t even log in rendering echo usless', 'Thomas Musson', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5303, 'Can\'t control alarms. Frustrating and pointless app. This horrible app is responsible for waking up my 5 year old in the middle of the night on a weekend and making him cry. Can I give it zero stars? Did Amazon fire the whole staff working on this POS and now nobody works on it? Nothing but expletives for this app.', 'Carrie Dahlby', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5304, 'New update makes it useless. Waste of money!', 'Lance Arnold', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5305, 'EDIT: Even worse now. How can such a great piece of hardware have such a terrible app? Non-responsive. Often can\'t find the Internet. Search function buried. No Favorites list. Very unintuitive design. And messaging? Really. Who cares? Wow, this app has really gone downhill. A full 90 seconds to sync to my Dot? No volume control? "Your Dot is disconnected" while it\'s playing music..... really? Really? Great product. Embarrassingly bad app.', 'Gregg LaPore', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5306, 'Great app!', 'Keith Mendenhall', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5307, 'Spent hours trying to link my Echo Dot to my Fire TV Stick, Amazon help pages don\'t tell you it doesn\'t work in the UK. Absolute rubbish, feel created and conned', 'Lee Blades', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5308, 'Awesome and Btw Alexa is way better than Siri', 'ICE X LIME YEET', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5309, 'It can do nothing useful on mobile...', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5310, 'This app continues to lockup.\nIt is the worst App.\nI have down load a new App weekly almost\nTo be able to use it.\nMakes me want throw Alez and Amazon out.\nLess than a one star rating.', 'Wished it would work', 'iTunes', 1, 'No Good', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 11:18:52'),
	(5311, 'Apparently the latest release disrupted the IHome and Alexa linking as my smart plugs no longer work with Alexa. Seems to be widespread.', 'Flskip', 'iTunes', 2, 'Latest Release', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 14:21:05'),
	(5312, 'If I’m listening to music, Audible, etc on my iPhone, and I get a call from the echo, it doesn’t make the music stop. Not only that, it won’t let me pause the music while on the call. \n\nI will be happy to change my review if the problem is solved.', 'Darin bearfan', 'iTunes', 1, 'Music keeps playing during call', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 14:58:17'),
	(5313, 'Features a volume control and multi room music are no longer available. The developers did a very poor job of this update', 'Bgtrucker', 'iTunes', 1, 'Poor update', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 15:31:55'),
	(5314, 'Why can I talk to Alexa in the Amazon or Amazon Music app but not in the Alexa app??\n\nThe nagging for enabling messaging/calling is pretty irritating as well.', 'Boarder2', 'iTunes', 3, 'Missing features', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 17:21:18'),
	(5315, 'Latest update is a step back. First, I could not get past the permission screen on my iPhone 10 with previous version, on my 7 works just fine. Latest update done on 01-28-18, the app closes within the first 3-5 seconds when deployed.', '@Ndrea1818', 'iTunes', 1, 'Force closes', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 18:37:19');
INSERT INTO `rating` (`id`, `review`, `author`, `review_source`, `rating`, `title`, `product_name`, `reviewed_date`) VALUES
	(5316, 'I used to use Alexa for music and my music unlimited says “app support not available”. How about some support? She’s just collecting dust now. Bummer.', 'randomhero2006', 'iTunes', 1, 'She’s useless now', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 21:15:31'),
	(5317, 'I have had the app for over 6 months and selecting music really doesn\'t work well. The way to select music sometimes is there and sometimes it is not. No way to save Favorites. Searching for channels is frustrating because it does not always let you select the item you are touching and grabs the item above or below. \nI would expect a lot more out of amazon. The echo is great but this is its flat tire!\n\nSeems to be losing functionality in the music apps. It will not give me a choice to add services any longer. On with tech support and they could not find it. Audible does not let me play my library and Again tech support could not find it. It could be a great product but they Have a way to go.', 'Usable news', 'iTunes', 2, 'Very basic and bug filled', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 22:58:24'),
	(5318, 'Could we get support for the iPhonex?', 'Golddawg', 'iTunes', 2, 'Needs iPhoneX Support, and better layout', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-29 02:13:22'),
	(5319, 'التطبيق يحتاج الى تحديث انه غير فعال .... اعلم جيداً ان لغتكم هي الانجليزية ولاتتحدثون اللغة العربية ... نجمة واحدة تكفي لعدم اهتمامكم بالتطبيق 🤪', 'From another planet', 'iTunes', 1, 'امازون اليكسا', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-29 06:39:57'),
	(5320, 'Please fix!', 'ctx143', 'iTunes', 1, 'Ver 221797 doesn’t save Start and End Request Sound setting', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-29 09:05:45'),
	(5321, 'I love', 'Michael Dixon', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5322, 'Won\'t connect to my spotify by voice. Waste of time', 'Daniel Plavenieks', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5323, 'Great app. Shows you in-depth information related to your Alexa requests, all very well formatted. Lets you review requests and report when Alexa misunderstood you.', 'Kevin Foley', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5324, 'You can not upload anymore your own songs, Alexa is useless now! If you could play songs from my phone at least via Dot device but that does not work either.  I do not know what to do with this device w/o ability to play your own songs.', 'Vaclav Novak', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5325, 'This app has become more functional with Ask Alexa added. A shortcut or widget would make it even better.', 'Earl DePass Jr.', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5326, 'This app is so incredibly slow. It takes way to long to do anything.', 'Steven Isley', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5327, 'Would love to have a widget on my home screen please. So can speak to echo without having to go in to a app.', 'Jonathan Jeffreys', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5328, 'Is there a way to change the alarm sound to one in your phone? Other than that, a great app!', 'Raajan_16', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5329, 'Interface is clunky & doesn\'t flow.', 'Gazza S', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
	(5330, 'When I can get it to play MY music (not Amazon Prime) and do most of the things I ask I\'ll let you know. Everytime my.internet drops out I have to set it up again! I am IT literate but can\'t understand how unhelpful this App is.', 'Teri Browett', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-28 00:00:00'),
