	(5389, 'I already have an echo. So why you don\'t want to let me get in', 'Greg Payne', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-30 00:00:00'),
	(5390, 'Was excited about the app getting the ability to talk to Alexa, however, so far I\'ve only had success making Alexa "beatbox".  Every normal command I give my Echo (add reminder, play WBEZ on TuneIn, etc.) it says device can\'t do... so what exactly is the point?!?  I have an Echo on my account, they should give the app the same abilities as the full device!  If they were able to do that I would also like the ability to add a widget to talk to Alexa without going in the app (replace Google)', 'Adeline Bailey', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-30 00:00:00'),
	(5391, 'Very poorly engineered the app works when it feels like it during voice training Alexa tells you to hit the next button which does not work you cannot get the next button and if you hit it it does absolutely nothing at all. Alexa really understands what I say I have replaced her with Google home', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-01-30 00:00:00'),
