	(5540, 'It’s getting a 1 star because I cant even get to this app to connect it to the new WiFi I have done all phone updates and keep checking if this app needs an update and nothing . Yet I hit the app it opens for half a second then goes back to my main screen so Alexa is useless right now .', 'Má Má', 'iTunes', 1, 'Not happy', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-04 12:37:59'),
