	(5576, 'Awesome app and I don\'t know what I would do without this, Specific app and I\'m really Satisfied with the apps I\'ve been installing on my new phone and I use most all of them on a weekly basis, thanks for everything and I will continue to use most of my installed apps!!!!!', 'Larry Harvey', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-05 00:00:00'),
	(5577, 'It mostly works. Often when you go to a section, like your shopping list for example, then go to a different section, the app will load the previous section, and continue to do so until you quit the app and restart it.', 'Jay McGinnis', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-05 00:00:00'),
	(5578, 'Basically pointless in Ireland', 'Daire O Connor', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-05 00:00:00'),
