	(6002, 'WATCH OUT PEOPLE PLEASE!! Echo Dot was hacked and our families security has been threatened. The hackers used the Echo as a gateway into ALL of our devices!! AMAZON WILL NOT HELP, BUT DID EXTEND THEIR APOLOGIES AND TOLD US THATS A RISK WE TAKE WITH INTERNET AND TOLD US TO DISCONNECT THE ECHO. What happened to customer service!! The credit bureau gets hacked and we at least get 2 years of free identity protection and other benefits.', 'Aleisha Sabino', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-18 00:00:00'),
	(6003, 'Has anyone else had problems with a "certificate error" upon opening the app? Google couldn\'t help me and Amazon isn\'t responding to my emails. Can anyone suggest a fix to this? I have repeatedly uninstalled and reinstalled both Alexa and WebView many times. Please help!!!', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-18 00:00:00'),
