	(6006, 'I don\'t know what Amazon did but they screwed up the Alexa app so much that I can\'t even use it on my phone! Call Amazon and now with the quickly diminishing customer service, I get no where! It used to work just fine and then the dreaded updates and so called fixes and now it doesn\'t work at all! Get with it Amazon!', 'Ruby Tuesday', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-19 00:00:00'),
