	(6069, 'If you\'re here, you\'ve already purchased an Alexa, and I wish you all the best. It really didn\'t work for me. Had a terrible time connecting to the Echo to the internet (could be that my Samsung Note 8 doesn\'t like connecting to the internet).  And the Spotify integration is pretty laughable.', 'Robert Richardson', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-23 00:00:00'),
	(6070, 'So slow. I cleared everything off my phone, killed all other apps, and I can\'t update settings for any of my devices. I\'m using a Galaxy. It shouldn\'t be this hard. Just terrible. The echo device is fine except when she tells me to use the app. Which is a lot more frequently than I would expect.', 'Sara Hansen-Lund', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-23 00:00:00'),
	(6071, 'The application is decent. It has come a long way in the last year. This is a work im progress but have to say it has been improving monthly with different things you can do. Such as turn your Alexa into a speaker phone. Turn your house into a automated home witb different devices like Nest, TCP-I or other like types to turn on and off lights,  holiday decorations. Have lights come on at dusk so you come home to a lit entryway and hallways! Also setup lighting to make a home look lived in by having lights go on and off in evening hours to make it look like you are going in and out of different rooms like when you ARE HOME! Sweet!', 'R P', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-23 00:00:00'),
