	(6103, 'Need to be able to control fire stick like USA. App is over complicated', 'Keith Semple', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-25 00:00:00'),
	(6104, 'When Alexa doesn\'t hear me correctly and I want to help give Amazon feedback to improve her, I can never find the card to do that.  The music feature doesn\'t allow you to search for your artist, you have to scroll and scroll and scroll till you find them. That is really sad that you can\'t simply type in what you are looking for and bam!', 'Josh Lyczkowski', 'GooglePlayStore', 3, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-25 00:00:00'),
	(6105, 'I live in a nursing home with not good wi-fi. Always get kicked off. This updates to Manual Set up. Frustrating! I can\'t get Amazon XXX or ORF & no idea what they mean or where they are! I\'ve had this for a couple years, LOVE her, but the re-set constantly is heartbreaking. Takes forever.', 'Renee Colbert', 'GooglePlayStore', 4, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-25 00:00:00'),
	(6106, 'I absolutely love Amazon Alexa. So awesome and everything is in one place!! Also really like how you can add features to your Amazon Echo.', 'Leah Lee', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-25 00:00:00'),
	(6107, 'Its been months and still can\'t DL the app. Wasted hours on phone w y\'all and nothing.  LG XPower w marshmallow', '', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-25 00:00:00'),
	(6108, 'This is a app that you can connect your Alexa device it makes you learn things and tell you things it is helpful', 'dominik wielosik', 'GooglePlayStore', 5, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-25 00:00:00'),
	(6109, 'Why did you take away the history of what songs were listened to in the app? It was there yesterday before the app updated. It now says to ask Alexa. I looked back at that when I was not home near Alexa, now I can\'t do that. Went to show a friend and it says it is not supported, ask Alexa, hard to do when you are not near it.   Newest issue, when I go to music, TuneIn in the app, it shows I\'m in a different city and state and Alexa can\'t find a station I have listened to since I got the Dot.', 'George Geller', 'GooglePlayStore', 2, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-26 00:00:00'),
	(6110, 'Worst app on my phone. Very slow to open, frequently crashes, seems to require me to sign in on a weekly basis at present, really let\'s down the Amazon ecosystem. The shopping list would be really useful if the Android app worked reliably', 'Paul French', 'GooglePlayStore', 1, '', 'Amazon Alexa', '2018-02-26 00:00:00');
